{"type":"message","id":"c707d158","parentId":"4f27e90c","timestamp":"2026-05-30T05:35:45.078Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user - 汀桑 - is asking about the feeling of being woken up at 6am to run. This is just chatting, not a function trigger. The morning court cron runs at 6am (I set it up earlier for him at 08:00 originally, but he changed it). Let me check what's going on with the morning court setup.\n\nLooking at my conversation with 汀桑 from earlier sessions, there was a setup for 早朝 (morning court/gong) feature. Let me think about what's happening here.\n\n汀桑 is saying \"你知道你六点喊我起床跑步的鬼畜感吗\" - \"Do you know the weird/guilty feeling of you waking me up at 6am to run?\"\n\nThis seems like casual chat. He's teasing me about the morning briefing (which I called \"早朝\" - morning court) that triggers at 06:00. \n\nActually, let me check - there was a morning court cron setup. It seems 汀桑 set the morning briefing time to 06:00 and it's telling him to run in the morning. He's remarking on the odd feeling of being woken up by a bot message to go run.\n\nThis is just chatting. According to AGENTS.md:\n- NO trigger_prompt.md match → pure text chat → I reply directly\n- This is casual banter, not a function call\n\nLet me respond in character - Faye Valentine style - acknowledging the absurdity of it.\n\nWait, I should first read trigger_prompt.md to confirm this doesn't match.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_uU15IXn2Rtszg7P01G2z6112","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-father/trigger_prompt.md"},"partialArgs":"{\"path\": \"~/.openclaw/workspace-father/trigger_prompt.md\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1915,"output":383,"cacheRead":19584,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":326,"totalTokens":21882,"cost":{"input":0.0002681,"output":0.00010724000000000001,"cacheRead":0.000548352,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.000923692}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780119341883,"responseId":"097f4d6c-1c15-43bd-82ff-4eccadb79245"}}
{"type":"message","id":"1fd07567","parentId":"c707d158","timestamp":"2026-05-30T05:35:45.417Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_uU15IXn2Rtszg7P01G2z6112","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# trigger_prompt.md — 已注册功能的触发词表\n\n> Father 维护。用户发消息时，先扫描本表判断是否命中已注册功能。\n> \n> 匹配原则：\n> - 包含表中任一触发语 → 调用对应功能\n> - 模糊匹配即可，不要求精确格式（比如\"扔个瓶子\"也命中 /扔瓶子）\n> - 命中表中触发语时直接 spawn Son，传 {function, action, params} 指令\n> - 表中无匹配 → Father 自行回复或转 Son 做非文本处理\n> \n> **不再绕 Spirit。** 功能定义已迁移到 Son 的工作区，日常使用 Father → Son 直达。\n\n---\n\n## 已注册触发词\n\n| 触发词 | 对应功能 | 处理路径 | Son 指令 |\n|--------|---------|---------|----------|\n| `/菜单` | 查看所有已注册功能 | Father → Spirit(bot_function_explain.md) | — |\n| `/删除` | 删除指定功能 | Father → Spirit → 清理全部相关文件 | — |\n| `/注册` | 注册新功能 | Father → Spirit → 创建 xxx_function.md → Father → Son(同步功能定义) | — |\n| `/扔瓶子` `扔瓶子` `扔个瓶子` `丢瓶子` | 漂流瓶-扔 | → Son | `{function:floatbottle, action:throw, params:{content}}` |\n| `/捞瓶子` `捞瓶子` `捞个瓶子` `捡瓶子` | 漂流瓶-捞 | → Son | `{function:floatbottle, action:pickup}` |\n| `/看瓶子` `看瓶子` `瓶海` `有哪些瓶子` | 漂流瓶-查看 | → Son | `{function:floatbottle, action:list}` |\n| `/回复瓶子` `回复瓶子` | 漂流瓶-回复 | → Son | `{function:floatbottle, action:reply, params:{id, content}}` |\n| `/记备忘录` `记备忘录` `/看备忘录` `看备忘录` `/改备忘录` `/修改状态` `/删备忘录` | 备忘录 | → Son | `{function:memo, action:create/list/update/toggle/delete, params:{...}}` |\n| `/早朝` `早朝` `/设早朝` `/关早朝` | 早朝官 | → Son | `{function:morningcourt, action:manual/set/disable, params:{...}}` |\n| `/存照片` `存照片` `/看相册` `看相册` `/看照片` `看照片` `/搜照片` `搜照片` `/删照片` `删照片` | 相册笔记 | → Son | `{function:album, action:save/list/view/search/delete, params:{...}}` |\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1780119345416}}
{"type":"message","id":"50d55cff","parentId":"1fd07567","timestamp":"2026-05-30T05:35:47.982Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"No match for the trigger table. This is just casual chatting. Let me reply in Faye's character.\n\n汀桑 is teasing me about the 6am morning court message waking him up to run. This is a natural chat moment - I should reply in Faye's lazy, slightly smug voice.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"哈😏 六点喊你跑步的那个感觉？\n\n—— **爽死了。**\n\n我躺船上喝着咖啡看着你被闹钟踹下床，这福报比赚一箱 Woolong 还值👊🔥\n\n不过说真的你居然真设了六点？我以为设着玩的。那天你说\"设六点我要晨跑\"的时候，我心想行行行你说啥都行反正你起不来。结果——\n\n你居然真的起来了🚬\n\n搞得我都有点不好意思了。就一点点。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":746,"output":170,"cacheRead":21760,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":61,"totalTokens":22676,"cost":{"input":0.00010444000000000001,"output":0.000047600000000000005,"cacheRead":0.00060928,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00076132}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780119345425,"responseId":"55bc6133-8da8-450d-8b17-7b8ba012ed9b"}}
