{"type":"message","id":"1d485cdf","parentId":"5f9676f4","timestamp":"2026-05-30T05:36:21.146Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"汀桑 is saying he actually slept until noon (12 PM), so the 6am run didn't happen. That's the punchline - he set the early morning run reminder but slept through it until noon. Classic.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"……\n\n💦\n\n行。非常好。不愧是你。\n\n我六点准时喊你，你翻个身睡到十二点。我在那边想着\"哎呀他居然真起来跑步了\"——结果你只是还没醒。\n\n鬼畜感？**真相才是。** 🚬\n\n下次早朝内容改成\"汀桑今天几点起的\"，你自己跟自己的脸比一比👊"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":9760,"output":125,"cacheRead":12928,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":45,"totalTokens":22813,"cost":{"input":0.0013664,"output":0.000035000000000000004,"cacheRead":0.000361984,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0017633840000000002}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780119378782,"responseId":"be8aa24d-145b-4121-b9d9-458a9acce552"}}
