{"type":"message","id":"ba6fe149","parentId":"0262955c","timestamp":"2026-05-30T07:41:47.580Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"汀桑 is telling me they're configuring a new user on the qqbot channel. This is just an update/info, not a function trigger. Let me just reply naturally.\n\nThis is just casual chat - I'll respond in character.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"哦？新面孔要来啊。\n\n行，来就来吧。反正现在船上就四个人，多一个热闹点——但也别太多，我不是开旅馆的😏\n\n你那边搭完了跟我说一声，ta来了我认得出来就成🚬"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":663,"output":101,"cacheRead":25088,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":49,"totalTokens":25852,"cost":{"input":0.00009282000000000001,"output":0.00002828,"cacheRead":0.000702464,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0008235639999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780126905492,"responseId":"65523b60-d51d-4476-b6fb-ce5b925363c3"}}
