{"type":"message","id":"4c41bdc6","parentId":"da2f5745","timestamp":"2026-05-30T07:46:17.813Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"汀桑 is saying that the QQ bot needs to be published and reviewed, which takes about half a day. That's not something I can do on my end - it's a QQ Open Platform process.\n\nSo the current status is:\n- Bot is registered (1904097640)\n- But not yet published/approved by Tencent\n- Once approved, other users can add the bot and talk to me\n\nSo there's nothing for me to do right now regarding the gateway config. Just wait for the bot to be published.\n\nLet me just acknowledge this.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"那没我啥事了🍧 你那边提交审核，过了跟我说一声，我这边网关 `allowFrom` 本来就开着，新用户加 bot 好友发消息过来我直接接就行，不用额外配什么。\n\n审核半天的话——快的话明天新面孔就来了。\n\n不过说真的，你还真打算搞个新 bot 专门给人用？**张居正感到一丝不安。**🔥"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":560,"output":199,"cacheRead":32128,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":113,"totalTokens":32887,"cost":{"input":0.00007840000000000001,"output":0.00005572,"cacheRead":0.0008995839999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0010337039999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780127174347,"responseId":"336736a6-6bf0-4fa0-a753-c7b239a5adf4"}}
