{"type":"message","id":"d55dd162","parentId":"088b626b","timestamp":"2026-05-30T07:56:24.469Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"汀桑 is asking me to register a new bot account (bot5) in the gateway configuration. The appid should be 1904097640 which he mentioned earlier. I need to update the openclaw.json to add a new account under channels.qqbot.accounts.\n\nBut writing to openclaw.json requires elevated permissions since it's a config change. Let me check if I can edit it directly or if I need approval.\n\nActually, let me look at the current accounts section again:\n\n```json\n\"accounts\": {\n    \"bot1\": {\n        \"appId\": \"1904085484\",\n        \"clientSecret\": \"***\"\n    },\n    \"bot2\": {\n        \"appId\": \"1904088180\",\n        \"clientSecret\": \"***\"\n    },\n    \"bot3\": {\n        \"appId\": \"1904090109\",\n        \"clientSecret\": \"***\"\n    },\n    \"bot4\": {\n        \"appId\": \"1904093350\",\n        \"clientSecret\": \"***\"\n    }\n}\n```\n\nBut I don't know the clientSecret for the new bot. 汀桑 only gave me the appid: 1904097640. I need the clientSecret too to register it. Also, I need to add a binding for it.\n\nWait, let me ask 汀桑 for the clientSecret... but actually, he just said \"现在注册bot5\" - he wants me to add it. He might have the secret handy.\n\nAlso, I need to update the openclaw.json which is a configuration file. Let me use the gateway tool to do this properly, or edit the file directly.\n\nActually, looking at the docs, I should use `openclaw gateway config.schema.lookup` or just edit the JSON file. Let me just edit the openclaw.json directly.\n\nWait, I need to ask for the clientSecret first. But maybe I should just read the current config and make the edit. Let me ask 汀桑 for the secret.\n\nActually, he only told me appid:1904097640. I need the clientSecret to register. Let me just ask.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"可以，不过我缺一个东西——**clientSecret**。\n\n你注册 bot5（1904097640）的时候腾讯那边给了个密钥，那个我需要写进配置里。你发我，我加进去，弹 `/approve` 你点一下就生效🍧\n\n然后我是直接在 `openclaw.json` 里加一个：\n```\nbot5: { appId: \"1904097640\", clientSecret: \"***\" }\n```\n再加一条路由绑定到 father，完事。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1585,"output":571,"cacheRead":32768,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":467,"totalTokens":34924,"cost":{"input":0.00022190000000000003,"output":0.00015988000000000002,"cacheRead":0.000917504,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001299284}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780127779334,"responseId":"0c1351dd-3f88-4ef1-a084-f0603297ac25"}}
