{"type":"message","id":"d216c46f","parentId":"88e3ae1b","timestamp":"2026-05-30T07:57:15.393Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"汀桑 has provided the clientSecret for the new bot5 (appId: 1904097640). Now I need to add it to the openclaw.json config file.\n\nThe secret is: 2pcQE3tjaRJB4ysnieaXVTSRRRSUWZcg\n\nLet me look at the current config structure for channels.qqbot.accounts:\n\n```json\n\"channels\": {\n    \"qqbot\": {\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"allowFrom\": [\"*\"],\n      \"groupAllowFrom\": [\"*\"],\n      \"accounts\": {\n        \"bot1\": {\n          \"appId\": \"1904085484\",\n          \"clientSecret\": \"***\"\n        },\n        \"bot2\": {\n          \"appId\": \"1904088180\",\n          \"clientSecret\": \"***\"\n        },\n        \"bot3\": {\n          \"appId\": \"1904090109\",\n          \"clientSecret\": \"***\"\n        },\n        \"bot4\": {\n          \"appId\": \"1904093350\",\n          \"clientSecret\": \"***\"\n        }\n      }\n    }\n  }\n```\n\nAnd for the bindings:\n```json\n\"bindings\": [\n    {\n      \"type\": \"route\",\n      \"agentId\": \"father\",\n      \"match\": {\n        \"channel\": \"qqbot\",\n        \"accountId\": \"bot1\"\n      }\n    },\n    ...\n]\n```\n\nI need to:\n1. Add bot5 to accounts\n2. Add a route binding for bot5 → father\n\nLet me use edit to modify the openclaw.json file. Since this is a JSON file, I need to be precise with the edits. Let me read the file again to get the exact content for editing.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好嘞，加进去。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_5fncMqgTWAzbIX9hNbys8452","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/openclaw.json"},"partialArgs":"{\"path\": \"/root/.openclaw/openclaw.json\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":691,"output":446,"cacheRead":33792,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":388,"totalTokens":34929,"cost":{"input":0.00009674000000000001,"output":0.00012488,"cacheRead":0.000946176,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001167796}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780127831949,"responseId":"fd5a24d9-f16d-4b40-871d-51557c257153"}}
