{"type":"message","id":"7419e088","parentId":"c47a6a1b","timestamp":"2026-05-30T07:59:54.020Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"汀桑 is showing me the conversation metadata again to make a point - probably confirming that my bot5 binding was already added correctly. But wait, they said \"Bindings也也要加 这个也绑定father\" - they're saying the bindings section also needs to have bot5 bound to father.\n\nBut I already added that! Let me verify by checking the bindings section in the config again.\n\nActually, I checked with `grep -A3 \"bot5\" /root/.openclaw/openclaw.json` and both the account entry AND the binding were found. So both are already in place. Let me confirm for the user.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"已经加了啊，你看看——\n\n```\n\"bindings\": [\n    { \"match\": { \"channel\": \"qqbot\", \"accountId\": \"bot1\" }, \"agentId\": \"father\" },\n    { \"match\": { \"channel\": \"qqbot\", \"accountId\": \"bot2\" }, \"agentId\": \"father\" },\n    { \"match\": { \"channel\": \"qqbot\", \"accountId\": \"bot3\" }, \"agentId\": \"father\" },\n    { \"match\": { \"channel\": \"qqbot\", \"accountId\": \"bot4\" }, \"agentId\": \"father\" },\n    { \"match\": { \"channel\": \"qqbot\", \"accountId\": \"bot5\" }, \"agentId\": \"father\" }\n]\n```\n\nbot5 的绑定也写进去了，不用再加了😏\n\n你现在要做的就一件事：**回腾讯开放平台提交审核**。过了之后把 bot5 的 QQ 号发给新用户，ta加好友说话就行了🔥"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":6129,"output":347,"cacheRead":34048,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":132,"totalTokens":40524,"cost":{"input":0.00085806,"output":0.00009716000000000001,"cacheRead":0.000953344,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001908564}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780127990504,"responseId":"8b6a9491-cdee-47c4-ad98-7607a24b2c77"}}
