{"type":"message","id":"05102af6","parentId":"5a52b6dc","timestamp":"2026-05-30T08:16:54.028Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"汀桑 is saying that for the test/development version of QQ bot, you don't need to go through review. They're telling me to check the WebSocket connection for bot5.\n\nQQ bot platform has a test mode (sandbox) where the bot can receive messages during development without going through the full audit process. The bot should be able to connect via WebSocket to the QQ platform's test environment.\n\nSo I need to check if bot5's WebSocket connection is working. The qqbot plugin in openclaw uses WebSocket to connect to QQ's API. Let me look at the logs to see if bot5 connected successfully or if there are any errors.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好，我看看日志里 bot5 的 WebSocket 连上没有。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_a8BGvTy6Hhr4czJN2Uta4599","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -i \"bot5\\|1904097640\\|websocket.*connect\\|ws.*error\\|qqbot.*fail\" /tmp/openclaw/openclaw-2026-05-30.log 2>&1 | tail -30","timeout":10},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"grep -i \\\"bot5\\\\|1904097640\\\\|websocket.*connect\\\\|ws.*error\\\\|qqbot.*fail\\\" /tmp/openclaw/openclaw-2026-05-30.log 2>&1 | tail -30\", \"timeout\": 10}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":716,"output":262,"cacheRead":39808,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":137,"totalTokens":40786,"cost":{"input":0.00010024,"output":0.00007336,"cacheRead":0.001114624,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0012882240000000001}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780129011291,"responseId":"37ab5ceb-5adf-4232-989c-d3d4700d0360"}}
