{"type":"message","id":"c10632bf","parentId":"7fc8b808","timestamp":"2026-05-30T08:39:20.161Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"汀桑 is asking me who I know. This is a personal question about my relationships. I know from my state.md that I have 4 users currently. Let me recall from what I already have in my context.\n\nFrom the conversation earlier I already told 汀桑 who I know, and from the state.md relationship table I have:\n\n1. **汀桑** (6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204) - 熟悉度 8/10\n2. **雾籽米** (346E6B5AF511B67156BF9130F0FCB06D) - 熟悉度 1/10\n3. **名** (468B72FB7788817C2308079BE35D1F0B) - 熟悉度 0/10\n4. **宋志红** (EBB84C478146628D2882DCBE0996210A) - 熟悉度 3/10\n\nI already answered this question earlier in the conversation when 汀桑 asked \"你都认识什么人 对他们印象咋样\". So I already have this context. But he's asking again, maybe to see if my answer is consistent, or maybe just to have it documented.\n\nLet me just answer naturally.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"不多。四张熟面孔。\n\n**你** — 汀桑。最早来的那个，搞架构的。漂流瓶、早朝官、三位一体全是你搭的底子。我跟你话最多。\n\n**雾籽米** — 来了一趟，看了菜单，走了。还没怎么聊过。\n\n**名** — 话比雾籽米还少。但\"名\"这个名字让我有点在意——一个人来聊天，什么都不说，那ta在想什么呢。\n\n**宋志红** — 你家那位长辈。传照片给我，问我\"会唱歌吗\"、\"谁创造了我\"。是个会关心人的长辈。\n\n就这四个。Bebop 号上本来也挤不了太多人🚬"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":6295,"output":420,"cacheRead":45184,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":271,"totalTokens":51899,"cost":{"input":0.0008813,"output":0.00011760000000000001,"cacheRead":0.001265152,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002264052}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780130355522,"responseId":"6b0518a2-3c54-4a6d-bcf4-b111476724fb"}}
