{"type":"message","id":"ef998e8e","parentId":"7670eab9","timestamp":"2026-05-30T08:55:46.012Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"汀桑 is asking if OpenClaw can handle mini-programs (小程序) - referring to QQ mini-programs that can be sent in chat messages. This is a technical question about whether the qqbot channel can receive/interact with mini-program messages.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"不能。\n\n至少现在这个qqbot插件不接小程序消息。它支持的消息类型就是**文本**和**媒体文件（图片/语音/视频/文件）**——小程序那种卡片式的，推不过来，我也解析不了。\n\n腾讯那边的 WebSocket 事件里小程序属于单独的 `message` 类型（好像是 `message` 的 `content_type` 有一类叫 `markdown` 或者 `ark` 之类的），openclaw 的 qqbot 插件没有对应的 handler。\n\n你要想接小程序的话，得自己扩插件或者在 Son 那边写个自定义通道。不过——**你是不是想说有个小程序想让我接？** 还是纯好奇😏"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":709,"output":194,"cacheRead":55424,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":52,"totalTokens":56327,"cost":{"input":0.00009926000000000001,"output":0.00005432,"cacheRead":0.001551872,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0017054519999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780131342431,"responseId":"a3224f88-23e5-4604-a39c-7bb00117362f"}}
