{"type":"message","id":"15291b0e","parentId":"22ed49f1","timestamp":"2026-05-30T10:11:28.159Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The sender_id is 6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204 which is 汀桑. And it looks like the clientSecret for bot6 was sent as \"RozxhEXdV8YjgQwD\" in the conversation, embedded in the metadata. Let me add bot6 to the config.\n\nWait, looking at the conversation flow - the user sent the metadata which includes \"RozxhEXdV8YjgQwD\" at the end. But this is untrusted metadata, not the user's actual message. Let me check if the actual user text contains the secret.\n\nActually, looking at the response more carefully, the untrusted metadata block is injected by the system. The user's actual message is just the metadata block. But the text \"RozxhEXdV8YjgQwD\" at the end seems to be the clientSecret they added as their message content.\n\nWait, I think the user is sending the metadata block that they see, and then at the very bottom of their message is \"RozxhEXdV8YjgQwD\" - which is the clientSecret for bot6.\n\nLet me proceed with adding bot6 to the config. The new bot info is:\n- appId: 1904097583\n- clientSecret: RozxhEXdV8YjgQwD","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_JeqwbBJoVVeS7uOtUZqG1509","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/openclaw.json","edits":[{"oldText":"        \"bot5\": {\n          \"appId\": \"1904097640\",\n          \"clientSecret\": \"***\"\n        }","newText":"        \"bot5\": {\n          \"appId\": \"1904097640\",\n          \"clientSecret\": \"***\"\n        },\n        \"bot6\": {\n          \"appId\": \"1904097583\",\n          \"clientSecret\": \"***\"\n        }"},{"oldText":"      \"type\": \"route\",\n      \"agentId\": \"father\",\n      \"match\": {\n        \"channel\": \"qqbot\",\n        \"accountId\": \"bot5\"\n      }\n    }","newText":"      \"type\": \"route\",\n      \"agentId\": \"father\",\n      \"match\": {\n        \"channel\": \"qqbot\",\n        \"accountId\": \"bot5\"\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"type\": \"route\",\n      \"agentId\": \"father\",\n      \"match\": {\n        \"channel\": \"qqbot\",\n        \"accountId\": \"bot6\"\n      }\n    }"}]},"partialArgs":"{\"path\": \"/root/.openclaw/openclaw.json\", \"edits\": [{\"oldText\":\"        \\\"bot5\\\": {\\n          \\\"appId\\\": \\\"1904097640\\\",\\n          \\\"clientSecret\\\": \\\"2pcQE3…WZcg\\\"\\n        }\",\"newText\":\"        \\\"bot5\\\": {\\n          \\\"appId\\\": \\\"1904097640\\\",\\n          \\\"clientSecret\\\": \\\"2pcQE3…WZcg\\\"\\n        },\\n        \\\"bot6\\\": {\\n          \\\"appId\\\": \\\"1904097583\\\",\\n          \\\"clientSecret\\\": \\\"RozxhE…gQwD\\\"\\n        }\"},{\"oldText\":\"      \\\"type\\\": \\\"route\\\",\\n      \\\"agentId\\\": \\\"father\\\",\\n      \\\"match\\\": {\\n        \\\"channel\\\": \\\"qqbot\\\",\\n        \\\"accountId\\\": \\\"bot5\\\"\\n      }\\n    }\",\"newText\":\"      \\\"type\\\": \\\"route\\\",\\n      \\\"agentId\\\": \\\"father\\\",\\n      \\\"match\\\": {\\n        \\\"channel\\\": \\\"qqbot\\\",\\n        \\\"accountId\\\": \\\"bot5\\\"\\n      }\\n    },\\n    {\\n      \\\"type\\\": \\\"route\\\",\\n      \\\"agentId\\\": \\\"father\\\",\\n      \\\"match\\\": {\\n        \\\"channel\\\": \\\"qqbot\\\",\\n        \\\"accountId\\\": \\\"bot6\\\"\\n      }\\n    }\"}]}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":464,"output":647,"cacheRead":55936,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":282,"totalTokens":57047,"cost":{"input":0.00006496,"output":0.00018116,"cacheRead":0.001566208,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001812328}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780135883408,"responseId":"681e7126-f041-4fed-b985-f98f07fd33fd"}}
