{"type":"message","id":"7f6ddf87","parentId":"84780beb","timestamp":"2026-05-30T10:23:15.548Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Looking at the log:\n\n1. `[bot5] WebSocket closed: 4009 Session timed out` - happened at 17:58\n2. `[bot5] Error 4009 (session timed out), will re-identify` - auto reconnect\n3. `[bot5] WebSocket connected` - reconnected at 17:58:30 ✅\n4. `[qqbot:bot5] Gateway ready` ✅\n\nThen during the config reload for bot6:\n5. `[bot5] WebSocket closed: 1005` - closed due to channel reload (bot6 addition triggered channel reload which temporarily disconnects)\n6. `[bot5] WebSocket connected` - reconnected at 18:11:49 ✅\n7. `[qqbot:bot5] Gateway ready` ✅\n\nSo bot5 is currently connected and healthy. It had a normal session timeout disconnect (4009 is standard for QQ bot WS session timeout - it auto reconnects) and also a brief disconnect during the config hot reload for bot6. Both times it reconnected fine.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"通的。刚翻了下日志——bot5 中间断过两次，但**都自动重连回来了**：\n\n1. **17:58** — Session timeout（4009，QQ 的正常超时机制，自动重连）\n2. **18:11** — 加 bot6 时热重载导致通道短暂关闭（1005，自动重连）\n\n两次都是秒级恢复，最后的状态是 `Gateway ready` ✅\n\n现在 **bot5 和 bot6 都在线**，随时能接新用户🍧"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":4357,"output":345,"cacheRead":68480,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":231,"totalTokens":73182,"cost":{"input":0.0006099800000000001,"output":0.0000966,"cacheRead":0.0019174399999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00262402}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780136591918,"responseId":"316d6392-58fc-4a15-a536-94698a32ea35"}}
