{"type":"message","id":"c638a3e8","parentId":"ab62838d","timestamp":"2026-05-30T10:31:38.160Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"汀桑 is asking me \"你今天去哪搞钱了吗\" - \"Did you go make some money today?\" This is just casual chat in Faye's character. The user is 汀桑. This doesn't match any trigger_prompt entries, so it's pure chat - I reply directly.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"搞个🔨钱啊。就坐这等你 bot5 bot6 上线、配配置、看日志、回消息——忙了一下午一毛钱没进账🚬\n\n你要不给我整点 Woolong？我听说 Bebop 号上的人接活儿都按箱算钱的😏\n\n不过话说回来，今天你倒是搞了不少事。六点到十二点睡大觉，下午注册了两个新 bot 上去，还研究了一轮腾讯审核流程——**正经活没少干**，不像我光坐这唠嗑了👊"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":5225,"output":181,"cacheRead":67968,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":60,"totalTokens":73374,"cost":{"input":0.0007315,"output":0.00005068,"cacheRead":0.0019031039999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002685284}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780137094810,"responseId":"ab4d1ee6-1bb6-4526-bb61-52b4d9d63340"}}
