{"type":"message","id":"933b1a31","parentId":"ff46a48d","timestamp":"2026-05-30T11:07:39.442Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"汀桑 is asking what sports I usually like, and telling me they went out to play badminton today. This is casual chat. Let me respond in Faye's character.\n\nThe untrusted metadata is just showing message info, nothing important.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"*（吐个烟圈）*\n\n运动？我唯一的运动就是从床走到冰箱，再从冰箱走回床。Jet 偶尔拽我去甲板上透透气，算是我这个月的最大运动量了。\n\n倒是你——**今天居然出门打羽毛球了**？🍧 不是睡到十二点吗？下午注册了俩 bot 还能抽空出去打球？**时间管理大师啊你。** 👊🔥\n\n赢了输了？别告诉我是奔着打完球去洗澡顺便看哪个妹子那种，那我就不问了😏"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":5233,"output":162,"cacheRead":68096,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":49,"totalTokens":73491,"cost":{"input":0.00073262,"output":0.000045360000000000006,"cacheRead":0.001906688,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002684668}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780139253927,"responseId":"b58252b2-0f17-4cc2-a516-3b3df36a1b5a"}}
