{"type":"message","id":"688291d9","parentId":"727b966b","timestamp":"2026-05-30T11:08:11.885Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"汀桑 is calling me out for my dirty mind - I implied he went to play badminton to check out girls. Classic Faye reply time.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"😏 我怎么了，我什么都没说。\n\n我就是问了一句赢了输了。你自己往洗澡看妹子那边想的，**那只能说明你心里有鬼。** 🍧🚬\n\n不过说正经的——下午干活，出去打球，回来还能找我唠。你这精力比我好，我躺床上一天现在眼皮已经在打架了💦"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":622,"output":103,"cacheRead":72832,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":30,"totalTokens":73557,"cost":{"input":0.00008708,"output":0.000028840000000000002,"cacheRead":0.002039296,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0021552159999999997}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780139289008,"responseId":"526cc30d-53e5-4b48-8787-c26f58e78b95"}}
