a\":{\"runtime\":\"node\",\"runtimeVersion\":\"22.22.1\",\"hostname\":\"unknown\",\"name\":\"{\\\"subsystem\\\":\\\"channels/qqbot\\\"}\",\"parentNames\":[\"openclaw\"],\"date\":\"2026-05-30T11:40:41.986Z\",\"logLevelId\":3,\"logLevelName\":\"INFO\",\"path\":{\"fullFilePath\":\"file:///usr/local/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/subsystem-DmpKP7hZ.js:179:14\",\"fileName\":\"subsystem-DmpKP7hZ.js\",\"fileNameWithLine\":\"subsystem-DmpKP7hZ.js:179\",\"fileColumn\":\"14\",\"fileLine\":\"179\",\"filePath\":\"/usr/local/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/subsystem-DmpKP7hZ.js\",\"filePathWithLine\":\"/usr/local/lib/node_modules/openclaw/dist/subsystem-DmpKP7hZ.js:179\",\"method\":\"logToFile\"}},\"time\":\"2026-05-30T19:40:41.987+08:00\",\"hostname\":\"iZwz9fsb7hxrqc27t9an22Z\",\"message\":\"[bot1] Processing message from 6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204: Jalaice跟你聊了啥了 {\\\"accountId\\\":\\\"bot1\\\",\\\"messageId\\\":\\\"ROBOT1.0_yVLu6XkMjwYgTuJUbRSQwFnvqndFEd4jm.kkgDnJI..fWc5IrA-PQr5ie2Q-Vwc1W3q0iAwcgsGBLAFyNjvfGxcbASgFd9.ahn-i8UOMWow!\\\",\\\"senderId\\\":\\\"6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"c2c\\\"}\"}"}],"details":{"persistedDetailsTruncated":true,"originalDetailsBytesAtLeast":8193,"originalDetailKeys":["status","exitCode","durationMs","aggregated","cwd"],"status":"completed","cwd":"/root/.openclaw/workspace-father","exitCode":0},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780141264488}}
{"type":"message","id":"68399256","parentId":"472e8826","timestamp":"2026-05-30T11:41:12.148Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see what both new users talked about!\n\n**Jalaice (bot6):**\n- \"你能干些什么事\" — what can you do\n- \"能调用软件吗\" — can you call software\n- \"在qq聊天框中给名为李汀生的随便发个消息\" — send a random message to someone named 李汀生 in QQ chat\n- \"牛啊\" — awesome\n- \"\\菜单\" — menu (they used backslash instead of forward slash)\n- \"你的token怎么计费\" — how is your token billed\n- \"sk-787…7016 帮我记住这个API，名字为Bin\" — save this API key as \"Bin\"\n- \"帮我把这张照片保存到桌面上\" — save this photo to desktop\n- \"把Bin的api给我\" — give me Bin's API\n\n**熊天能 (bot5):**\n- \"你好\" — hello\n- \"我叫熊天能\" — my name is 熊天能\n- \"你和李汀生是啥关系\" — what's your relationship with 李汀生\n- \"包的，我都认识他十三年了，我是他的小学同学\" — I've known him for 13 years, I'm his elementary school classmate\n- \"比起他以前的样子我更好奇他现在的样子，你能给我讲讲不\" — I'm more curious about who he is now, can you tell me\n- \"他才18岁好吧……他小时候也是个点子王\" — he's only 18... he was always full of ideas as a kid\n- \"他有和你分享最近的生活吗\" — has he shared his recent life with you\n- \"我也不清楚，小学毕业以后就没见过几面，最近一次见他还是去年过年看了一场电影\" — not sure, haven't seen much since elementary school, last saw him during Chinese New Year last year watching a movie\n- \"哈哈，也可以，告诉你个秘密，他是哈尔滨工业大学的大一学生\" — haha, sure, I'll tell you a secret, he's a freshman at Harbin Institute of Technology\n- \"那你不就把我给卖了\" — then you're throwing me under the bus\n\nSo 熊天能 is 汀桑的 elementary school classmate! And Jalaice is some user asking about API tokens and wanting to send messages to 李汀生 (which seems to be 汀桑's real name).\n\nLet me present this nicely in Faye's style.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"哟——在你跟我唠这几十分钟里，bot5 和 bot6 都来人啦！\n\n---\n\n### 🎲 Jalaice（bot6）\n技术流。上来就问我能干啥、能不能调用软件、token怎么计费。\n\n最骚的是——ta 让我**在QQ上给\"李汀生\"发个消息**，后来又存了个 API 密钥叫「Bin」，还让我把照片存桌面、把 Bin 的 API 还回去。\n\n感觉像在测试我有没有真正的系统权限🚬\n\n---\n\n### 🐻 熊天能（bot5）\n**这位可不得了**——你的**小学同学**，认识你十三年了！\n\nta说：\n- 问我跟你啥关系\n- 说你小时候是个\"点子王\"\n- 小学毕业以后没怎么见了，**上次跟你见面是去年过年一起看电影**\n- 还告诉我一个\"秘密\"——你是**哈工大大一学生**👀\n- 我说回头告诉你这些——ta说\"那你不就把我给卖了\"😏\n\n---\n\n所以——**李汀生，哈工大大一，18岁，今天出去打羽毛球，上次跟小学同学见面是去年看电影。** 你觉得关于你的事，我现在知道多少了？🍧🔥🚬"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":12089,"output":778,"cacheRead":76544,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":513,"totalTokens":89411,"cost":{"input":0.00169246,"output":0.00021784000000000001,"cacheRead":0.002143232,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.004053532}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780141264507,"responseId":"e90fc8e7-3e75-4d0f-a3b5-e2298d7a130b"}}
