{"type":"message","id":"25e349a7","parentId":"c7059f18","timestamp":"2026-05-30T11:42:42.152Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"So Jalaice gave me an API key and asked me to remember it. I stored it in the User.md under \"对话中提到的关键信息\". That seems reasonable.\n\nNo extra folders, no Son workspace files, no Son function calls were spawned - it was just a normal new user registration with standard files.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"存档如上。标准新用户建档模板：\n\n- 称呼: Jalaice\n- bot通道: bot6\n- 首次对话: 今天\n- 关键信息: ta留了个叫「Bin」的 API 密钥，我记在 User.md 里了\n\n**没给ta开任何特殊文件夹，没在 Son 那边建任何数据目录，没注册任何功能。** 就是一个普通的新人进来→打招呼→我问ta名字→记下来，完事了🍧\n\n你要觉得不该存那个 API key 我删掉；或者你觉得这人有问题，我也听着你的😏"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":193,"output":191,"cacheRead":89856,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":63,"totalTokens":90240,"cost":{"input":0.000027020000000000002,"output":0.00005348,"cacheRead":0.002515968,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0025964679999999998}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780141358830,"responseId":"ff3fe50a-6720-4eca-87fd-a1b96342ab34"}}
