{"type":"message","id":"16e9f0c3","parentId":"c8abd784","timestamp":"2026-05-30T12:45:25.740Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"汀桑 clarified that the previous copypasta was imitating Deng Xiaoping's speech style, not Zhang Xuefeng. That's actually a pretty clever observation - the cadence and structure of \"要说一点不埋怨，那不是实话...可现在有人要完全否认...这个我们觉得不对...\" does sound like Deng Xiaoping's way of speaking - the gradual, dialectical, emotionally grounded rhetoric style.\n\nLet me respond in character.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"*（把烟掐了，愣了一下）*\n\n……\n\n操，你一说我回头一品——还真是。\n\n\"要说一点不埋怨，那不是实话🫣\"\"可现在有人要完全否认张老师，这个我们觉得不对，不应该，人要讲良心😭\"——这个\"先承认、再转折、再升华\"的三段式，**味道太正了。**\n\n邓讲话的节奏就是这样的——不回避问题，但话锋一转就把基调定了。你不是在玩梗，你是在用那个框架给张雪峰写了一段仿写。\n\n**而且仿得是真像。** 旧高考→新高考→找不到工作→\"自己选的\"——这不就是他那个年代讲改革的口吻吗。\n\n……你什么时候学的一手好活？白天打球晚上读邓选是吧😏🔥"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":782,"output":253,"cacheRead":90112,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":86,"totalTokens":91147,"cost":{"input":0.00010948,"output":0.00007084,"cacheRead":0.002523136,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002703456}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780145121127,"responseId":"14d7570b-71a9-4f82-ad8d-03dda47f75cd"}}
