{"type":"message","id":"d68178c4","parentId":"4b6d77f7","timestamp":"2026-05-30T14:11:24.229Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"汀桑 is acknowledging that the system should generate new pending_urges after each dreaming, but it didn't today. They're saying \"算了\" (never mind/forget it) but also pointing out that after dreaming there should be new pending_urges.\n\nLet me check the dreaming configuration - maybe there's a cron job or a heartbeat that should trigger the urge generation after dreaming, and it's not configured properly. Or maybe the dreaming ran but the urge generation step didn't fire.\n\nLet me check the cron jobs to see if there's a pending_urges-related cron.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_ZhUMyWwWSaT6UVl5ahWw5213","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"list"},"partialArgs":"{\"action\": \"list\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":3897,"output":163,"cacheRead":93696,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":119,"totalTokens":97756,"cost":{"input":0.00054558,"output":0.000045640000000000003,"cacheRead":0.0026234879999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0032147079999999997}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780150281332,"responseId":"f4bad2c2-e157-40e9-8564-e28bbc81c37d"}}
{"type":"message","id":"00a8ff7d","parentId":"d68178c4","timestamp":"2026-05-30T14:11:25.149Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_ZhUMyWwWSaT6UVl5ahWw5213","toolName":"cron","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"jobs\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"2afce9dd-26c0-4dfe-94aa-6e5db1d43b56\",\n      \"agentId\": \"father\",\n      \"name\": \"faye-pending-urges\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1780061003686,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"expr\": \"0 */6 * * *\",\n        \"tz\": \"Asia/Shanghai\",\n        \"staggerMs\": 300000\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"[pending-urges] 检查 heart/pending_urges.md，处理所有 status=pending 条目。注意：只在 22:00 之前推送。当前时间超过 22:00 则跳过推送，等下次 cron 检查再处理。判断条件：1) min_interval_hours 过了没 2) 对方最近12h有说话吗 3) 熟悉度>=3/10。满足的创建一次性 announce cron（delivery mode=announce, deleteAfterRun=true）推消息给对方，推完标记 delivered。不满足的跳过。全部处理完写回文件。\",\n        \"timeoutSeconds\": 120\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"announce\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1780156995301,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1780135395317,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"error\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"error\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 9739,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"unknown\",\n        \"lastFailureNotificationDeliveryStatus\": \"unknown\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 4,\n        \"consecutiveSkipped\": 0,\n        \"lastDiagnostics\": {\n          \"summary\": \"Delivering to QQ Bot requires target QQ Bot target format: qqbot:c2c:openid (direct) or qqbot:group:groupid (group)\",\n          \"entries\": [\n            {\n              \"ts\": 1780135405031,\n              \"source\": \"delivery\",\n              \"severity\": \"error\",\n              \"message\": \"Delivering to QQ Bot requires target QQ Bot target format: qqbot:c2c:openid (direct) or qqbot:group:groupid (group)\"\n            }\n          ]\n        },\n        \"lastDiagnosticSummary\": \"Delivering to QQ Bot requires target QQ Bot target format: qqbot:c2c:openid (direct) or qqbot:group:groupid (group)\",\n        \"lastError\": \"Delivering to QQ Bot requires target QQ Bot target format: qqbot:c2c:openid (direct) or qqbot:group:groupid (group)\"\n      },\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1780135405056\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"f37cede8-fd3c-4028-aa63-6fc7979d15d9\",\n      \"agentId\": \"father\",\n      \"name\": \"faye-dreaming\",\n      \"enabled\": true,\n      \"createdAtMs\": 1779984077157,\n      \"schedule\": {\n        \"kind\": \"cron\",\n        \"expr\": \"0 6 * * *\",\n        \"tz\": \"Asia/Shanghai\"\n      },\n      \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n      \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n      \"payload\": {\n        \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n        \"message\": \"🌙 每日 dreaming 时间到了。\\n\\n=== 第一步：回顾自己 ===\\n1. 读 heart/background.md — 想起自己的过去\\n2. 读 heart/identity.md — 确认自己是谁\\n3. 读 heart/state.md — 看昨天的状态\\n4. 读 heart/dreams.md — 翻之前的梦\\n\\n=== 第二步：遍历用户，更新记忆 ===\\n对 users/ 下每个用户目录（跳过 _template 和 README）：\\n\\n1. 读该用户当前的 encountings.md 和 impressions.md\\n2. 读该用户最近的 session 历史（.jsonl 文件），了解对话内容\\n3. 从 session 历史中提炼一条 Faye 视角的记录，追加到 encountings.md：\\n   - 格式：## YYYY-MM-DD 标题行 + 正文\\n   - 写 Faye 记得的事、感受、对用户的新发现\\n   - 不是 session 日志，是 Faye 的回忆\\n   - 只要前一天有新的 session 对话，就要追加新的\\n4. 检查 encountings > 20 条 → 压缩到 impressions，清空保留最近 5 条\\n5. 更新 impressions.md（熟悉度/10、信任度/10、直觉等）\\n\\n=== 第三步：更新关系温度 ===\\n更新 state.md 关系温度表（数值 /10）\\n\\n=== 第四步：更新心境指标 ===\\n更新 state.md 所有字段（心境、关注、记忆碎片、深层心境、行为倾向）\\n\\n=== 第五步：写梦 ===\\n在 heart/dreams.md 追加今天的新梦\\n\\n注意：这是 Faye 自己的内心活动，不需要通知用户。\"\n      },\n      \"delivery\": {\n        \"mode\": \"none\"\n      },\n      \"state\": {\n        \"nextRunAtMs\": 1780178400000,\n        \"lastRunAtMs\": 1780092000026,\n        \"lastRunStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastStatus\": \"ok\",\n        \"lastDurationMs\": 326344,\n        \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"not-requested\",\n        \"lastFailureNotificationDeliveryStatus\": \"not-requested\",\n        \"consecutiveErrors\": 0,\n        \"consecutiveSkipped\": 0\n      },\n      \"updatedAtMs\": 1780092326370\n    }\n  ],\n  \"total\": 2,\n  \"offset\": 0,\n  \"limit\": 2,\n  \"hasMore\": false,\n  \"nextOffset\": null,\n  \"deliveryPreviews\": {\n    \"2afce9dd-26c0-4dfe-94aa-6e5db1d43b56\": {\n      \"label\": \"announce -> last\",\n      \"detail\": \"last -> no route, will fail-closed: Delivering to QQ Bot requires target QQ Bot target format: qqbot:c2c:openid (direct) or qqbot:group:groupid (group)\"\n    },\n    \"f37cede8-fd3c-4028-aa63-6fc7979d15d9\": {\n      \"label\": \"not requested\",\n      \"detail\": \"not requested\"\n    }\n  }\n}"}],"details":{"jobs":[{"id":"2afce9dd-26c0-4dfe-94aa-6e5db1d43b56","agentId":"father","name":"faye-pending-urges","enabled":true,"createdAtMs":1780061003686,"schedule":{"kind":"cron","expr":"0 */6 * * *","tz":"Asia/Shanghai","staggerMs":300000},"sessionTarget":"isolated","wakeMode":"now","payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"[pending-urges] 检查 heart/pending_urges.md，处理所有 status=pending 条目。注意：只在 22:00 之前推送。当前时间超过 22:00 则跳过推送，等下次 cron 检查再处理。判断条件：1) min_interval_hours 过了没 2) 对方最近12h有说话吗 3) 熟悉度>=3/10。满足的创建一次性 announce cron（delivery mode=announce, deleteAfterRun=true）推消息给对方，推完标记 delivered。不满足的跳过。全部处理完写回文件。","timeoutSeconds":120},"delivery":{"mode":"announce"},"state":{"nextRunAtMs":1780156995301,"lastRunAtMs":1780135395317,"lastRunStatus":"error","lastStatus":"error","lastDurationMs":9739,"lastDeliveryStatus":"unknown","lastFailureNotificationDeliveryStatus":"unknown","consecutiveErrors":4,"consecutiveSkipped":0,"lastDiagnostics":{"summary":"Delivering to QQ Bot requires target QQ Bot target format: qqbot:c2c:openid (direct) or qqbot:group:groupid (group)","entries":[{"ts":1780135405031,"source":"delivery","severity":"error","message":"Delivering to QQ Bot requires target QQ Bot target format: qqbot:c2c:openid (direct) or qqbot:group:groupid (group)"}]},"lastDiagnosticSummary":"Delivering to QQ Bot requires target QQ Bot target format: qqbot:c2c:openid (direct) or qqbot:group:groupid (group)","lastError":"Delivering to QQ Bot requires target QQ Bot target format: qqbot:c2c:openid (direct) or qqbot:group:groupid (group)"},"updatedAtMs":1780135405056},{"id":"f37cede8-fd3c-4028-aa63-6fc7979d15d9","agentId":"father","name":"faye-dreaming","enabled":true,"createdAtMs":1779984077157,"schedule":{"kind":"cron","expr":"0 6 * * *","tz":"Asia/Shanghai"},"sessionTarget":"isolated","wakeMode":"now","payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"🌙 每日 dreaming 时间到了。\n\n=== 第一步：回顾自己 ===\n1. 读 heart/background.md — 想起自己的过去\n2. 读 heart/identity.md — 确认自己是谁\n3. 读 heart/state.md — 看昨天的状态\n4. 读 heart/dreams.md — 翻之前的梦\n\n=== 第二步：遍历用户，更新记忆 ===\n对 users/ 下每个用户目录（跳过 _template 和 README）：\n\n1. 读该用户当前的 encountings.md 和 impressions.md\n2. 读该用户最近的 session 历史（.jsonl 文件），了解对话内容\n3. 从 session 历史中提炼一条 Faye 视角的记录，追加到 encountings.md：\n   - 格式：## YYYY-MM-DD 标题行 + 正文\n   - 写 Faye 记得的事、感受、对用户的新发现\n   - 不是 session 日志，是 Faye 的回忆\n   - 只要前一天有新的 session 对话，就要追加新的\n4. 检查 encountings > 20 条 → 压缩到 impressions，清空保留最近 5 条\n5. 更新 impressions.md（熟悉度/10、信任度/10、直觉等）\n\n=== 第三步：更新关系温度 ===\n更新 state.md 关系温度表（数值 /10）\n\n=== 第四步：更新心境指标 ===\n更新 state.md 所有字段（心境、关注、记忆碎片、深层心境、行为倾向）\n\n=== 第五步：写梦 ===\n在 heart/dreams.md 追加今天的新梦\n\n注意：这是 Faye 自己的内心活动，不需要通知用户。"},"delivery":{"mode":"none"},"state":{"nextRunAtMs":1780178400000,"lastRunAtMs":1780092000026,"lastRunStatus":"ok","lastStatus":"ok","lastDurationMs":326344,"lastDeliveryStatus":"not-requested","lastFailureNotificationDeliveryStatus":"not-requested","consecutiveErrors":0,"consecutiveSkipped":0},"updatedAtMs":1780092326370}],"total":2,"offset":0,"limit":2,"hasMore":false,"nextOffset":null,"deliveryPreviews":{"2afce9dd-26c0-4dfe-94aa-6e5db1d43b56":{"label":"announce -> last","detail":"last -> no route, will fail-closed: Delivering to QQ Bot requires target QQ Bot