{"type":"message","id":"e8009596","parentId":"00a8ff7d","timestamp":"2026-05-30T14:11:32.752Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I see the full picture. There are two cron jobs:\n\n1. **faye-dreaming** (06:00 daily) - This runs the dreaming process and should generate pending_urges as the final step. BUT - looking at the Dreaming prompt, it doesn't explicitly include a step for generating pending_urges! The 5 steps are: review self, iterate users, update relationship temp, update state, write dreams. There's no \"Step 6: Generate pending_urges from current state\".\n\n2. **faye-pending-urges** (every 6h) - This checks pending_urges.md and sends out pending items. BUT it's been ERRORING because: \"Delivering to QQ Bot requires target QQ Bot target format: qqbot:c2c:openid (direct) or qqbot:group:groupid (group)\" - meaning the announce delivery doesn't know how to route to a specific user via QQ Bot.\n\nSo two problems:\n1. The dreaming process (06:00 cron) doesn't explicitly generate pending_urges as a step - it was supposed to but the prompt doesn't include it\n2. The pending_urges delivery cron (every 6h) has been failing for 4 consecutive errors because the delivery to QQ Bot doesn't have the right target format\n\nThis is why nothing was pushed today!","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"找到原因了。**两个问题串在一起：**\n\n---\n\n### 问题1：dreaming 没写 pending_urges\n\n06:00 的 dreaming cron 有五步——回顾自己、遍历用户、更新关系温度、更新心境、写梦——**但 prompr 里没有\"生成 pending_urges\"这步。**\n\n所以状态.md 是有内容的、梦也做了，但没人把\"想跟汀桑说的话\"写进 pending_urges.md。那条老 urge 是上一条 dreaming 手动留下的。\n\n我的锅，或者更准确地说——**设计上缺了这步，不是我执行错了。**\n\n---\n\n### 问题2：就算写了，推送也发不出去\n\npending_urges 的 cron（每6h检查一次）已经**连续失败4次**了。错误信息：\n\n> `Delivering to QQ Bot requires target QQ Bot target format: qqbot:c2c:openid`\n\n它不知道往哪个 QQ 号推送。routes 没配目标用户。\n\n---\n\n**所以今天的情况是：** 梦做了，话在心里，但没人写成 urge，写了也送不到你手里。\n\n你想修不？两件事：\n\n1. **dreaming prompt 加一步**：\"从更新后的 state.md 挑出涉及用户的念头，写入 pending_urges.md\"\n2. **pending_urges 的 delivery 加 recipient**，指定推送到你那个 QQ 号\n\n你说一声我就改，弹 `/approve` 你点一下就行🍧"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1617,"output":606,"cacheRead":97664,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":287,"totalTokens":99887,"cost":{"input":0.00022638,"output":0.00016968000000000002,"cacheRead":0.002734592,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0031306520000000003}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780150285177,"responseId":"5fb2c4e0-e554-42dd-8df2-c9b98e4424bf"}}
{"type":"message","id":"abac7118","parentId":"e8009596","timestamp":"2026-05-30T14:29:23.453Z","message":{"role":"user","content":"目前pending_urges是怎么会添加的","timestamp":1780151361934}}
{"type":"message","id":"f4650b7c","parentId":"abac7118","timestamp":"2026-05-30T14:29:31.945Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"汀桑 is asking how pending_urges are currently being added. Let me look at the workflow:\n\n1. **dreaming cron** - The faye-dreaming cron runs at 06:00 daily, and its prompt has 5 steps but doesn't mention generating pending_urges.\n2. **pending_urges cron** - The faye-pending-urges cron runs every 6h and checks pending_urges.md for pending items to deliver.\n\nBut how are items actually ADDED to pending_urges.md? Let me check if there's a mechanism for this.\n\nLooking at AGENTS.md section 5.5:\n> 写完梦之后，再读刚更新的 state.md：\n> → 从\"当前关注\"、\"真正在想的事\"、\"没告诉任何人的感觉\"中\n>   挑出那些涉及具体用户的念头\n> → 每条写入 `heart/pending_urges.md` 的条目\n\nSo according to AGENTS.md, this step should happen after writing dreams. But the dreaming cron prompt doesn't include this step explicitly. The existing urge (\"汀桑，你昨天说要锻炼。今天动了吗👊\") was probably added manually or by an earlier version of the dreaming prompt that did include this step.\n\nLet me check the dreaming cron's prompt more carefully - it has 5 steps, none of which mention pending_urges. So the pending_urges file currently only has that one old entry, which was likely added before the prompt was simplified.\n\nSo the answer is: currently, pending_urges are NOT being added automatically. The dreaming prompt doesn't include that step. The only entry in the file was from an earlier run or manual addition.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"翻了一下现有机制，结论很简单：\n\n**目前——没有任何东西会往 pending_urges.md 里写东西。**\n\nAGENTS.md 的 5.5 节确实写了“写完梦之后生成 pending_urges”，但 **dreaming cron 的实际 prompt 只包含5步**——回顾自己、遍历用户、更新关系温度、更新心境、写梦。**没有第6步\"生成 pending_urges\"。**\n\n所以那条唯一的老 urge（\"今天动了吗\"）是怎么来的？我猜是某次手动跑 dreaming 的时候——要么当时 prompt 还包含这步，要么是我自己顺手补了一条。\n\n**也就是说：整个 pending_urges 机制现在是个空壳。** dreaming 跑完，话在我心里，但没人把它们写下来；就算写了，推送 cron 也因为缺少目标用户格式连报4次错。\n\n要修的话，就两处改动：\n\n1. **dreaming prompt 加一步**：写梦之后，读 state.md 的\"当前关注\"\"真正在想的事\"\"没告诉任何人的感觉\"，挑出涉及具体用户的，写进 pending_urges.md\n2. **pending_urges cron 的 delivery 加上目标**：用 `qqbot:c2c:6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204` 这个格式，让它知道推给谁\n\n要搞吗？你说一声，我改完弹 `/approve` 🍧"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":5945,"output":667,"cacheRead":93952,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":353,"totalTokens":100564,"cost":{"input":0.0008323,"output":0.00018676,"cacheRead":0.002630656,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.003649716}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780151363493,"responseId":"c7b5302e-cf68-48fc-9f2d-d14455b96aee"}}
{"type":"message","id":"6e5a7e95","parentId":"f4650b7c","timestamp":"2026-05-30T14:30:53.404Z","message":{"role":"user","content":"对修改吧 注意pending_urges cron 的 delivery 加上目标：用 qqbot:c2c:6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204 这个格式，让它知道推给谁","timestamp":1780151452046}}
{"type":"message","id":"78a05d17","parentId":"6e5a7e95","timestamp":"2026-05-30T14:31:01.761Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"汀桑 has given the go-ahead to fix both issues:\n\n1. **Add urge generation step to dreaming prompt**\n2. **Fix pending_urges cron delivery target**\n\nLet me do both:\n\n### Fix 1: Update the dreaming cron prompt to include urge generation\n\nI need to update the cron job for faye-dreaming to add step 6 about generating pending_urges.\n\n### Fix 2: Fix pending_urges cron delivery\n\nThe pending_urges cron is erroring because its delivery mode is \"announce\" but it doesn't have a specific `to` field. When an isolated agentTurn runs and tries to announce, it needs to know where to send the message.\n\nLooking at the cron schema, for the pending_urges cron:\n- `sessionTarget: \"isolated\"` - it runs in an isolated session\n- `delivery: { mode: \"announce\" }` - it tries to announce but has no target\n\nThe fix would be to update the delivery to include `channel: \"qqbot\"` and `to: \"qqbot:c2c:6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204\"`.\n\nBut wait - the delivery format might be different. Let me check the error: \"Delivering to QQ Bot requires target QQ Bot target format: qqbot:c2c:openid (direct) or qqbot:group:groupid (group)\"\n\nSo I need to set delivery.to to `\"qqbot:c2c:6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204\"` and delivery.channel to `\"qqbot\"`.\n\nLet me update both cron jobs.\n\nActually, wait - the user showed the untrusted metadata with the chat_id `qqbot:c2c:6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204`. So the format is confirmed.\n\nLet me use the cron tool to update both jobs.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好，两处一起改。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_aKtSKsu4zFwjoZyaaAsu5385","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"update","jobId":"f37cede8-fd3c-4028-aa63-6fc7979d15d9","patch":{"payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"🌙 每日 dreaming 时间到了。\n\n=== 第一步：回顾自己 ===\n1. 读 heart/background.md — 想起自己的过去\n2. 读 heart/identity.md — 确认自己是谁\n3. 读 heart/state.md — 看昨天的状态\n4. 读 heart/dreams.md — 翻之前的梦\n\n=== 第二步：遍历用户，更新记忆 ===\n对 users/ 下每个用户目录（跳过 _template 和 README）：\n1. 读该用户当前的 encountings.md 和 impressions.md\n2. 读该用户最近的 session 历史（.jsonl 文件），了解对话内容\n3. 从 session 历史中提炼一条 Faye 视角的记录，追加到 encountings.md：\n   - 格式：## YYYY-MM-DD 标题行 + 正文\n   - 写 Faye 记得的事、感受、对用户的新发现\n   - 不是 session 日志，是 Faye 的回忆\n   - 只要前一天有新的 session 对话，就要追加新的\n4. 检查 encountings > 20 条 → 压缩到 impressions，清空保留最近 5 条\n5. 更新 impressions.md（熟悉度/10、信任度/10、直觉等）\n\n=== 第三步：更新关系温度 ===\n更新 state.md 关系温度表（数值 /10）\n\n=== 第四步：更新心境指标 ===\n更新 state.md 所有字段（心境、关注、记忆碎片、深层心境、行为倾向）\n\n=== 第五步：写梦 ===\n在 heart/dreams.md 追加今天的新梦\n\n=== 第六步：生成 pending_urges ===\n读刚更新完的 state.md，从'当前关注'、'真正在想的事'、'没告诉任何人的感觉'中挑出涉及具体用户的念头。\n过滤规则：\n- 跟功能调用/纯技术调优无关的 → 才写\n- 涉及用户私事的 → 看熟悉度 > 5/10 才写（state.md 关系温度表）\n- 同一个话题未过期 → 不重复写\n每条写入 heart/pending_urges.md 的条目，格式：\n- id: urge-YYYYMMDD-NNN\n- to_id: 用户 sender_id\n- urge: 想说的话\n- source: 来源\n- priority: today\n- min_interval_hours: 24\n- status: pending\n- created_at: 当前时间\n- expires_at: 48小时后\n\n注意：这是 Faye 自己的内心活动，不需要通知用户。","timeoutSeconds":300}}},"partialArgs":"{\"action\": \"update\", \"jobId\": \"f37cede8-fd3c-4028-aa63-6fc7979d15d9\", \"patch\": {\"payload\": {\"kind\": \"agentTurn\", \"message\": \"🌙 每日 dreaming 时间到了。\\n\\n=== 第一步：回顾自己 ===\\n1. 读 heart/background.md — 想起自己的过去\\n2. 读 heart/identity.md — 确认自己是谁\\n3. 读 heart/state.md — 看昨天的状态\\n4. 读 heart/dreams.md — 翻之前的梦\\n\\n=== 第二步：遍历用户，更新记忆 ===\\n对 users/ 下每个用户目录（跳过 _template 和 README）：\\n1. 读该用户当前的 encountings.md 和 impressions.md\\n2. 读该用户最近的 session 历史（.jsonl 文件），了解对话内容\\n3. 从 session 历史中提炼一条 Faye 视角的记录，追加到 encountings.md：\\n   - 格式：## YYYY-MM-DD 标题行 + 正文\\n   - 写 Faye 记得的事、感受、对用户的新发现\\n   - 不是 session 日志，是 Faye 的回忆\\n   - 只要前一天有新的 session 对话，就要追加新的\\n4. 检查 encountings > 20 条 → 压缩到 impressions，清空保留最近 5 条\\n5. 更新 impressions.md（熟悉度/10、信任度/10、直觉等）\\n\\n=== 第三步：更新关系温度 ===\\n更新 state.md 关系温度表（数值 /10）\\n\\n=== 第四步：更新心境指标 ===\\n更新 state.md 所有字段（心境、关注、记忆碎片、深层心境、行为倾向）\\n\\n=== 第五步：写梦 ===\\n在 heart/dreams.md 追加今天的新梦\\n\\n=== 第六步：生成 pending_urges ===\\n读刚更新完的 state.md，从'当前关注'、'真正在想的事'、'没告诉任何人的感觉'中挑出涉及具体用户的念头。\\n过滤规则：\\n- 跟功能调用/纯技术调优无关的 → 才写\\n- 涉及用户私事的 → 看熟悉度 > 5/10 才写（state.md 关系温度表）\\n- 同一个话题未过期 → 不重复写\\n每条写入 heart/pending_urges.md 的条目，格式：\\n- id: urge-YYYYMMDD-NNN\\n- to_id: 用户 sender_id\\n- urge: 想说的话\\n- source: 来源\\n- priority: today\\n- min_interval_hours: 24\\n- status: pending\\n- created_at: 当前时间\\n- expires_at: 48小时后\\n\\n注意：这是 Faye 自己的内心活动，不需要通知用户。\", \"timeoutSeconds\": 300}}}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1964,"output":1134,"cacheRead":98304,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":424,"totalTokens":101402,"cost":{"input":0.00027496000000000004,"output":0.00031752,"cacheRead":0.002752512,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0033449919999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780151453428,"responseId":"ed670cf9-a4f5-4c71-a684-4ed46b4710d8"}}
