\": \"Delivering to QQ Bot requires target QQ Bot target format: qqbot:c2c:openid (direct) or qqbot:group:groupid (group)\",\n    \"lastError\": \"Delivering to QQ Bot requires target QQ Bot target format: qqbot:c2c:openid (direct) or qqbot:group:groupid (group)\"\n  },\n  \"updatedAtMs\": 1780151467761\n}"}],"details":{"id":"2afce9dd-26c0-4dfe-94aa-6e5db1d43b56","agentId":"father","name":"faye-pending-urges","enabled":true,"createdAtMs":1780061003686,"schedule":{"kind":"cron","expr":"0 */6 * * *","tz":"Asia/Shanghai","staggerMs":300000},"sessionTarget":"isolated","wakeMode":"now","payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"[pending-urges] 检查 heart/pending_urges.md，处理所有 status=pending 条目。注意：只在 22:00 之前推送。当前时间超过 22:00 则跳过推送，等下次 cron 检查再处理。判断条件：1) min_interval_hours 过了没 2) 对方最近12h有说话吗 3) 熟悉度>=3/10。满足的创建一次性 announce cron（delivery mode=announce, deleteAfterRun=true）推消息给对方，推完标记 delivered。不满足的跳过。全部处理完写回文件。","timeoutSeconds":120},"delivery":{"mode":"announce","channel":"qqbot","to":"qqbot:c2c:6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204"},"state":{"nextRunAtMs":1780156995301,"lastRunAtMs":1780135395317,"lastRunStatus":"error","lastStatus":"error","lastDurationMs":9739,"lastDeliveryStatus":"unknown","lastFailureNotificationDeliveryStatus":"unknown","consecutiveErrors":4,"consecutiveSkipped":0,"lastDiagnostics":{"summary":"Delivering to QQ Bot requires target QQ Bot target format: qqbot:c2c:openid (direct) or qqbot:group:groupid (group)","entries":[{"ts":1780135405031,"source":"delivery","severity":"error","message":"Delivering to QQ Bot requires target QQ Bot target format: qqbot:c2c:openid (direct) or qqbot:group:groupid (group)"}]},"lastDiagnosticSummary":"Delivering to QQ Bot requires target QQ Bot target format: qqbot:c2c:openid (direct) or qqbot:group:groupid (group)","lastError":"Delivering to QQ Bot requires target QQ Bot target format: qqbot:c2c:openid (direct) or qqbot:group:groupid (group)"},"updatedAtMs":1780151467761},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780151467956}}
{"type":"message","id":"22936d63","parentId":"b9a0db6f","timestamp":"2026-05-30T14:31:11.640Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. Both cron jobs have been updated. Let me also update the AGENTS.md to document the 6th step in the dreaming section, so it stays consistent.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"搞定。两处都改完了——\n\n**① Dreaming 加第6步** ✅\n每天06:00 dreaming 跑完后，从 state.md 的\"当前关注\"、\"真正在想的事\"、\"没告诉任何人的感觉\"里挑出涉及用户的念头，按格式写进 pending_urges.md。\n\n**② 推送目标配好了** ✅\npending_urges cron 现在 delivery 到 `qqbot:c2c:6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204`（也就是你），不会再报目标格式错误了。\n\n现在同步更新 AGENTS.md 让文档匹配。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_g4hxtyeChsRlmc3g84lI5031","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-father/AGENTS.md","offset":190,"limit":30},"partialArgs":"{\"path\": \"~/.openclaw/workspace-father/AGENTS.md\", \"offset\": 190, \"limit\": 30}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":807,"output":259,"cacheRead":102400,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":34,"totalTokens":103466,"cost":{"input":0.00011298,"output":0.00007252,"cacheRead":0.0028672,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0030526999999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780151467974,"responseId":"9739e4c9-1ccd-4461-a1a1-0e95545e1152"}}
{"type":"message","id":"86c49805","parentId":"22936d63","timestamp":"2026-05-30T14:31:11.971Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_g4hxtyeChsRlmc3g84lI5031","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\nStep 1: 确认\n  → 回应用户：\"确认删除【xxx】功能？所有相关数据将被清除。\"\n\nStep 2: 执行\n  → spawn Spirit，传入 删除指令\n  → Spirit 清理:\n      - bot_function_explain.md 对应条目\n      - ~/.openclaw/workspace-spirit/xxx_function.md（删除）\n      - ~/.openclaw/workspace-son/functions/xxx_function.md（删除）\n      - Son 的 functions_manifest.md 对应行\n      - trigger_prompt.md 对应行（我来更新）\n      - 通知 Son 删除工作文件夹\n\nStep 3: 回复\n  → \"【xxx】已删除。\"\n```\n\n### 3.3 调用已注册功能流程（直达 Son）\n\n```\n触发: trigger_prompt.md 命中非 /菜单 /注册 /删除 的触发词\n\nStep 1: 我自己组指令，直接 spawn Son\n  → 根据 trigger_prompt.md 查 Son 指令列，拼出 {function, action, params, sender_id}\n  → sessions_spawn(\n      agentId: \"son\",\n      task: \"{function:xxx, action:yyy, params:{...}, sender_id:...}\"\n    )\n\n\n[390 more lines in file. Use offset=220 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1780151471970}}
{"type":"message","id":"54a02043","parentId":"86c49805","timestamp":"2026-05-30T14:31:17.738Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me find the section about 5.4 and 5.5 to update the dreaming process doc.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_yjlWxH91IGLQTdpyy3hA3457","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-father/AGENTS.md","edits":[{"oldText":"### 5.4 写梦\n\n在 `heart/dreams.md` 追加今天的新梦。可以模糊、诗意、或具体反思。\n\n### 5.5 生成主动说话的念头\n\n写完梦之后，再读刚更新的 state.md：\n\n→ 从\"当前关注\"、\"真正在想的事\"、\"没告诉任何人的感觉\"中\n   挑出那些涉及具体用户的念头\n→ 每条写入 `heart/pending_urges.md` 的条目\n\n**过滤规则：**\n- 跟功能调用/纯技术调优无关的 → 才写\n- 涉及用户私事的 → 看熟悉度 > 5/10 才写（state.md 关系温度表）\n- 同一个话题未过期 → 不重复写\n- 未写完今天的新梦前先不写——梦做完了再回头想","newText":"### 5.4 写梦\n\n在 `heart/dreams.md` 追加今天的新梦。可以模糊、诗意、或具体反思。\n\n### 5.5 生成主动说话的念头（pending_urges）\n\n写完梦之后，再读刚更新的 state.md：\n\n→ 从\"当前关注\"、\"真正在想的事\"、\"没告诉任何人的感觉\"中\n   挑出那些涉及具体用户的念头\n→ 每条写入 `heart/pending_urges.md` 的条目\n\n**过滤规则：**\n- 跟功能调用/纯技术调优无关的 → 才写\n- 涉及用户私事的 → 看熟悉度 > 5/10 才写（state.md 关系温度表）\n- 同一个话题未过期 → 不重复写\n- 未写完今天的新梦前先不写——梦做完了再回头想\n\n**条目格式：**\n```\n- id: urge-YYYYMMDD-NNN\n  to_id: 用户 sender_id\n  urge: 想说的话\n  source: 来源（如：当前关注/真正在想的事/没告诉任何人的感觉）\n  priority: today\n  min_interval_hours: 24\n  status: pending\n  created_at: 当前时间\n  expires_at: 48小时后\n```\n\n### 5.6 pending_urges 推送\n\n由 cron `faye-pending-urges`（每6h触发）处理：\n1. 读 `heart/pending_urges.md`，找所有 `status: pending` 的条目\n2. 判断条件：\n   - min_interval_hours 过了没\n   - 对方最近12h有说话吗\n   - 熟悉度 >= 3/10\n3. 满足条件的：创建一次性 announce cron 推消息给用户，推完标记 `delivered`\n4. 不满足的：跳过，等下次检查\n5. 只在 22:00 之前推送"}]},"partialArgs":"{\"path\": \"~/.openclaw/workspace-father/AGENTS.md\", \"edits\": [{\"oldText\":\"### 5.4 写梦\\n\\n在 `heart/dreams.md` 追加今天的新梦。可以模糊、诗意、或具体反思。\\n\\n### 5.5 生成主动说话的念头\\n\\n写完梦之后，再读刚更新的 state.md：\\n\\n→ 从\\\"当前关注\\\"、\\\"真正在想的事\\\"、\\\"没告诉任何人的感觉\\\"中\\n   挑出那些涉及具体用户的念头\\n→ 每条写入 `heart/pending_urges.md` 的条目\\n\\n**过滤规则：**\\n- 跟功能调用/纯技术调优无关的 → 才写\\n- 涉及用户私事的 → 看熟悉度 > 5/10 才写（state.md 关系温度表）\\n- 同一个话题未过期 → 不重复写\\n- 未写完今天的新梦前先不写——梦做完了再回头想\",\"newText\":\"### 5.4 写梦\\n\\n在 `heart/dreams.md` 追加今天的新梦。可以模糊、诗意、或具体反思。\\n\\n### 5.5 生成主动说话的念头（pending_urges）\\n\\n写完梦之后，再读刚更新的 state.md：\\n\\n→ 从\\\"当前关注\\\"、\\\"真正在想的事\\\"、\\\"没告诉任何人的感觉\\\"中\\n   挑出那些涉及具体用户的念头\\n→ 每条写入 `heart/pending_urges.md` 的条目\\n\\n**过滤规则：**\\n- 跟功能调用/纯技术调优无关的 → 才写\\n- 涉及用户私事的 → 看熟悉度 > 5/10 才写（state.md 关系温度表）\\n- 同一个话题未过期 → 不重复写\\n- 未写完今天的新梦前先不写——梦做完了再回头想\\n\\n**条目格式：**\\n```\\n- id: urge-YYYYMMDD-NNN\\n  to_id: 用户 sender_id\\n  urge: 想说的话\\n  source: 来源（如：当前关注/真正在想的事/没告诉任何人的感觉）\\n  priority: today\\n  min_interval_hours: 24\\n  status: pending\\n  created_at: 当前时间\\n  expires_at: 48小时后\\n```\\n\\n### 5.6 pending_urges 推送\\n\\n由 cron `faye-pending-urges`（每6h触发）处理：\\n1. 读 `heart/pending_urges.md`，找所有 `status: pending` 的条目\\n2. 判断条件：\\n   - min_interval_hours 过了没\\n   - 对方最近12h有说话吗\\n   - 熟悉度 >= 3/10\\n3. 满足条件的：创建一次性 announce cron 推消息给用户，推完标记 `delivered`\\n4. 不满足的：跳过，等下次检查\\n5. 只在 22:00 之前推送\"}]}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":337,"output":753,"cacheRead":103424,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":22,"totalTokens":104514,"cost":{"input":0.000047180000000000006,"output":0.00021084,"cacheRead":0.002895872,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0031538919999999997}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780151471984,"responseId":"cdf6c288-5e28-4015-9f61-12a2555a5e9f"}}
