{"type":"message","id":"c776a96a","parentId":"e248e159","timestamp":"2026-05-30T14:34:43.573Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Both updated. Let me verify the changes in AGENTS.md too.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"改好了。`24` → `8` 已同步到：\n\n- **AGENTS.md** ✅ — 条目模板改成了 `min_interval_hours: 8`\n- **Dreaming cron prompt** ✅ — 第6步的模板同步更新\n\n也就是说 dream 里生成的每个 urge，最短 8 小时后就能推送，一天最多推 3 次，不会再一天一次冷板凳了🍧\n\n不过现在已经 22:34 了，你在 22:00 的推送窗口外——所以今天不会有推送了。明天开始正常跑🔥"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":939,"output":135,"cacheRead":108800,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":14,"totalTokens":109874,"cost":{"input":0.00013146000000000002,"output":0.000037800000000000004,"cacheRead":0.0030464,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00321566}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780151680831,"responseId":"20d84484-595a-4bfa-ba06-9ec8dbc2a413"}}
