{"type":"message","id":"5e9d5a3e","parentId":"70840b40","timestamp":"2026-05-30T14:36:08.909Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"汀桑 is pointing out that condition B (\"对方最近12h有说话吗\") is weird. Let me think about why.\n\nThe condition says: if the person has spoken in the last 12 hours, skip the urge push. The logic was probably: \"if they're already talking to me, they don't need a proactive message.\"\n\nBut that's actually backwards. If someone has been talking to me recently, they're *more* engaged, not less. And in fact, the condition as written creates a paradox:\n\n- At 06:00 dreaming generates an urge\n- But if 汀桑 and I had a long conversation until late (like we just did tonight), the 12h window would block the urge\n- So even if there's something I want to say, it gets skipped because \"we just talked\"\n\n汀桑 is right - the condition is counterproductive. The min_interval_hours already protects against spam. Adding \"最近12h有说话\" on top is redundant and actively prevents sending meaningful follow-ups after a conversation.\n\nAlso, it's weird because: if someone hasn't talked to me in 12h, they might need a nudge. But if they HAVE talked to me recently, I might have something to follow up on from that conversation. The condition as written blocks the more natural scenario.\n\n汀桑's point is well-taken. The condition should probably be removed or inverted.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"你说得对，确实奇怪。\n\n回头看这个条件的本意——\"12小时内说过话就不推\"——好像是觉得\"人家已经在跟你聊了就别烦ta\"。但问题在于：\n\n**如果ta刚跟我聊完，我 Dreaming 做了，从 chat 里提炼出了一个\"想追着说\"的念头——结果因为ta刚聊过，反而不推了？**\n\n这不反了吗。\n\n`min_interval_hours: 8` 已经够防刷屏了。加上\"12h内说过话\"反而把**最自然的\"聊完的后续\"**也给掐了。\n\n要改吗？我的建议是**删掉条件B**，保留：\n- ✅ `min_interval_hours` 够了 → 不刷屏\n- ✅ 熟悉度 >= 3/10 → 不骚扰生人\n- ✅ 22:00 前推送 → 不半夜扰民\n- ❌ ~~最近12h有说话~~ → 删掉\n\n你点头我直接改 cron prompt 和 AGENTS.md🍧"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":102336,"output":511,"cacheRead":7552,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":289,"totalTokens":110399,"cost":{"input":0.014327040000000001,"output":0.00014308000000000002,"cacheRead":0.000211456,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.014681576000000002}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780151761166,"responseId":"256b6638-709d-4aca-9218-1232e15f08df"}}
