{"type":"message","id":"fde9d218","parentId":"785ea281","timestamp":"2026-05-30T14:43:50.490Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"汀桑 has confirmed he wants me to go ahead with the merged A+C方案. He also wants to keep:\n- ✅ 熟悉度 >= 3/10\n- ✅ 22:00 前推送\n\nSo the final conditions for pending_urges will be:\n\n**Generation (Dreaming Step 6):**\n- urge 生成时带 timing 字段 (morning/casual/afterthought/quiet)\n- 跟功能调用/纯技术调优无关的 → 才写\n- 涉及用户私事的 → 看熟悉度 > 5/10 才写（state.md 关系温度表）\n- 同一个话题未过期 → 不重复写\n\n**推送 (cron faye-pending-urges):**\n- 熟悉度 >= 3/10\n- 22:00 前推送\n- 当前时段匹配对应的 timing 类型\n- 同一用户一天最多一条\n\nI need to update:\n1. AGENTS.md - update 5.5 (urge format with timing), 5.6 (push logic)\n2. Dreaming cron prompt (Step 6 - add timing field)\n3. Pending-urges cron prompt (update the check logic)\n\nLet me do all three.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_Dd3yVGdtH5rwleriFx0r8158","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-father/AGENTS.md","edits":[{"oldText":"**条目格式：**\n```\n- id: urge-YYYYMMDD-NNN\n  to_id: 用户 sender_id\n  urge: 想说的话\n  source: 来源（如：当前关注/真正在想的事/没告诉任何人的感觉）\n  priority: today\n  min_interval_hours: 8\n  status: pending\n  created_at: 当前时间\n  expires_at: 48小时后\n```\n\n### 5.6 pending_urges 推送\n\n由 cron `faye-pending-urges`（每6h触发）处理：\n1. 读 `heart/pending_urges.md`，找所有 `status: pending` 的条目\n2. 判断条件：\n   - min_interval_hours 过了没\n   - 对方最近12h有说话吗\n   - 熟悉度 >= 3/10\n3. 满足条件的：创建一次性 announce cron 推消息给用户，推完标记 `delivered`\n4. 不满足的：跳过，等下次检查\n5. 只在 22:00 之前推送","newText":"**条目格式：**\n```\n- id: urge-YYYYMMDD-NNN\n  to_id: 用户 sender_id\n  urge: 想说的话\n  source: 来源（如：当前关注/真正在想的事/没告诉任何人的感觉）\n  timing: morning | casual | afterthought | quiet\n  priority: today\n  status: pending\n  created_at: 当前时间\n  expires_at: 48小时后\n```\n\n**timing 说明：**\n- `morning` — 适合早上说的（提醒、督促、早安类）\n- `casual` — 随便聊聊的日常话题\n- `afterthought` — 上次对话的后续回味\n- `quiet` — 对方超过24h没说话时才推的挂念类\n\n### 5.6 pending_urges 推送\n\n由 cron `faye-pending-urges`（每6h触发）处理：\n1. 读 `heart/pending_urges.md`，找所有 `status: pending` 的条目\n2. 按用户分组，每个用户一天最多推一条\n3. 逐条判断：\n   - 熟悉度 >= 3/10\n   - 只在 22:00 之前推送\n   - 当前时段匹配 urge 的 timing：\n     - 06:00-09:00 → 优先推 timing=morning\n     - 14:00-20:00 → 优先推 timing=casual / afterthought\n     - 08:00-22:00 →（无匹配时）随便推一条 pending\n     - timing=quiet 仅当用户超过24h未发言时触发，不绑时间段\n4. 满足所有条件的：创建一次性 announce cron（delivery.mode=announce, channel=qqbot, deleteAfterRun=true）推消息给用户，推完标记 `delivered`\n5. 不满足的：跳过，等下次 cron 检查"}]},"partialArgs":"{\"path\": \"~/.openclaw/workspace-father/AGENTS.md\", \"edits\": [{\"oldText\":\"**条目格式：**\\n```\\n- id: urge-YYYYMMDD-NNN\\n  to_id: 用户 sender_id\\n  urge: 想说的话\\n  source: 来源（如：当前关注/真正在想的事/没告诉任何人的感觉）\\n  priority: today\\n  min_interval_hours: 8\\n  status: pending\\n  created_at: 当前时间\\n  expires_at: 48小时后\\n```\\n\\n### 5.6 pending_urges 推送\\n\\n由 cron `faye-pending-urges`（每6h触发）处理：\\n1. 读 `heart/pending_urges.md`，找所有 `status: pending` 的条目\\n2. 判断条件：\\n   - min_interval_hours 过了没\\n   - 对方最近12h有说话吗\\n   - 熟悉度 >= 3/10\\n3. 满足条件的：创建一次性 announce cron 推消息给用户，推完标记 `delivered`\\n4. 不满足的：跳过，等下次检查\\n5. 只在 22:00 之前推送\",\"newText\":\"**条目格式：**\\n```\\n- id: urge-YYYYMMDD-NNN\\n  to_id: 用户 sender_id\\n  urge: 想说的话\\n  source: 来源（如：当前关注/真正在想的事/没告诉任何人的感觉）\\n  timing: morning | casual | afterthought | quiet\\n  priority: today\\n  status: pending\\n  created_at: 当前时间\\n  expires_at: 48小时后\\n```\\n\\n**timing 说明：**\\n- `morning` — 适合早上说的（提醒、督促、早安类）\\n- `casual` — 随便聊聊的日常话题\\n- `afterthought` — 上次对话的后续回味\\n- `quiet` — 对方超过24h没说话时才推的挂念类\\n\\n### 5.6 pending_urges 推送\\n\\n由 cron `faye-pending-urges`（每6h触发）处理：\\n1. 读 `heart/pending_urges.md`，找所有 `status: pending` 的条目\\n2. 按用户分组，每个用户一天最多推一条\\n3. 逐条判断：\\n   - 熟悉度 >= 3/10\\n   - 只在 22:00 之前推送\\n   - 当前时段匹配 urge 的 timing：\\n     - 06:00-09:00 → 优先推 timing=morning\\n     - 14:00-20:00 → 优先推 timing=casual / afterthought\\n     - 08:00-22:00 →（无匹配时）随便推一条 pending\\n     - timing=quiet 仅当用户超过24h未发言时触发，不绑时间段\\n4. 满足所有条件的：创建一次性 announce cron（delivery.mode=announce, channel=qqbot, deleteAfterRun=true）推消息给用户，推完标记 `delivered`\\n5. 不满足的：跳过，等下次 cron 检查\"}]}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1180,"output":1028,"cacheRead":109696,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":261,"totalTokens":111904,"cost":{"input":0.0001652,"output":0.00028784000000000004,"cacheRead":0.003071488,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.003524528}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780152222485,"responseId":"1b4a565d-9bce-499c-b513-500178abc92b"}}
