对方超过24h没说话时才推的挂念类\n- priority: today\n- status: pending\n- created_at: 当前时间\n- expires_at: 48小时后\n\n注意：这是 Faye 自己的内心活动，不需要通知用户。","timeoutSeconds":300},"delivery":{"mode":"none"},"state":{"nextRunAtMs":1780178400000,"lastRunAtMs":1780092000026,"lastRunStatus":"ok","lastStatus":"ok","lastDurationMs":326344,"lastDeliveryStatus":"not-requested","lastFailureNotificationDeliveryStatus":"not-requested","consecutiveErrors":0,"consecutiveSkipped":0},"updatedAtMs":1780152236712},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780152236911}}
{"type":"message","id":"721ba460","parentId":"686b596a","timestamp":"2026-05-30T14:44:00.843Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. Now update the pending-urges cron prompt to reflect the new logic.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_9n6UihG4jm4nvwoi6fgA3450","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"update","jobId":"2afce9dd-26c0-4dfe-94aa-6e5db1d43b56","patch":{"payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"[pending-urges] 检查 heart/pending_urges.md，处理所有 status=pending 条目。\n\n处理逻辑：\n1. 按用户（to_id）分组，每个用户一天最多推一条\n2. 对每个用户的 pending 条目逐条判断：\n   - 熟悉度 >= 3/10（从 state.md 关系温度表读取）\n   - 只在 22:00 之前推送。当前时间超过 22:00 则跳过推送，等下次 cron 检查再处理\n   - 当前时段匹配 urge 的 timing：\n     - 06:00-09:00 → 优先推 timing=morning 的条目\n     - 14:00-20:00 → 优先推 timing=casual / afterthought 的条目\n     - 08:00-22:00 →（无匹配）随便推一条 pending\n     - timing=quiet 仅当用户超过24h未发言时触发，不绑时间段\n3. 满足所有条件的：\n   - 创建一次性 announce cron（delivery.mode=announce, channel=qqbot, to=qqbot:c2c:用户sender_id, deleteAfterRun=true）推消息给对方\n   - 将本条 urge 标记为 delivered\n4. 不满足的：跳过，等下次检查\n全部处理完写回文件。","timeoutSeconds":120}}},"partialArgs":"{\"action\": \"update\", \"jobId\": \"2afce9dd-26c0-4dfe-94aa-6e5db1d43b56\", \"patch\": {\"payload\":{\"kind\":\"agentTurn\",\"message\":\"[pending-urges] 检查 heart/pending_urges.md，处理所有 status=pending 条目。\\n\\n处理逻辑：\\n1. 按用户（to_id）分组，每个用户一天最多推一条\\n2. 对每个用户的 pending 条目逐条判断：\\n   - 熟悉度 >= 3/10（从 state.md 关系温度表读取）\\n   - 只在 22:00 之前推送。当前时间超过 22:00 则跳过推送，等下次 cron 检查再处理\\n   - 当前时段匹配 urge 的 timing：\\n     - 06:00-09:00 → 优先推 timing=morning 的条目\\n     - 14:00-20:00 → 优先推 timing=casual / afterthought 的条目\\n     - 08:00-22:00 →（无匹配）随便推一条 pending\\n     - timing=quiet 仅当用户超过24h未发言时触发，不绑时间段\\n3. 满足所有条件的：\\n   - 创建一次性 announce cron（delivery.mode=announce, channel=qqbot, to=qqbot:c2c:用户sender_id, deleteAfterRun=true）推消息给对方\\n   - 将本条 urge 标记为 delivered\\n4. 不满足的：跳过，等下次检查\\n全部处理完写回文件。\",\"timeoutSeconds\":120}}}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1030,"output":435,"cacheRead":112640,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":17,"totalTokens":114105,"cost":{"input":0.0001442,"output":0.0001218,"cacheRead":0.0031539199999999997,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00341992}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780152236935,"responseId":"428051f7-8ff3-4669-93ec-667763e17bcb"}}
{"type":"message","id":"7cc3413e","parentId":"721ba460","timestamp":"2026-05-30T14:44:01.353Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_9n6UihG4jm4nvwoi6fgA3450","toolName":"cron","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"id\": \"2afce9dd-26c0-4dfe-94aa-6e5db1d43b56\",\n  \"agentId\": \"father\",\n  \"name\": \"faye-pending-urges\",\n  \"enabled\": true,\n  \"createdAtMs\": 1780061003686,\n  \"schedule\": {\n    \"kind\": \"cron\",\n    \"expr\": \"0 */6 * * *\",\n    \"tz\": \"Asia/Shanghai\",\n    \"staggerMs\": 300000\n  },\n  \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n  \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n  \"payload\": {\n    \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n    \"message\": \"[pending-urges] 检查 heart/pending_urges.md，处理所有 status=pending 条目。\\n\\n处理逻辑：\\n1. 按用户（to_id）分组，每个用户一天最多推一条\\n2. 对每个用户的 pending 条目逐条判断：\\n   - 熟悉度 >= 3/10（从 state.md 关系温度表读取）\\n   - 只在 22:00 之前推送。当前时间超过 22:00 则跳过推送，等下次 cron 检查再处理\\n   - 当前时段匹配 urge 的 timing：\\n     - 06:00-09:00 → 优先推 timing=morning 的条目\\n     - 14:00-20:00 → 优先推 timing=casual / afterthought 的条目\\n     - 08:00-22:00 →（无匹配）随便推一条 pending\\n     - timing=quiet 仅当用户超过24h未发言时触发，不绑时间段\\n3. 满足所有条件的：\\n   - 创建一次性 announce cron（delivery.mode=announce, channel=qqbot, to=qqbot:c2c:用户sender_id, deleteAfterRun=true）推消息给对方\\n   - 将本条 urge 标记为 delivered\\n4. 不满足的：跳过，等下次检查\\n全部处理完写回文件。\",\n    \"timeoutSeconds\": 120\n  },\n  \"delivery\": {\n    \"mode\": \"announce\",\n    \"channel\": \"qqbot\",\n    \"to\": \"qqbot:c2c:6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204\"\n  },\n  \"state\": {\n    \"nextRunAtMs\": 1780156995301,\n    \"lastRunAtMs\": 1780135395317,\n    \"lastRunStatus\": \"error\",\n    \"lastStatus\": \"error\",\n    \"lastDurationMs\": 9739,\n    \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"unknown\",\n    \"lastFailureNotificationDeliveryStatus\": \"unknown\",\n    \"consecutiveErrors\": 4,\n    \"consecutiveSkipped\": 0,\n    \"lastDiagnostics\": {\n      \"summary\": \"Delivering to QQ Bot requires target QQ Bot target format: qqbot:c2c:openid (direct) or qqbot:group:groupid (group)\",\n      \"entries\": [\n        {\n          \"ts\": 1780135405031,\n          \"source\": \"delivery\",\n          \"severity\": \"error\",\n          \"message\": \"Delivering to QQ Bot requires target QQ Bot target format: qqbot:c2c:openid (direct) or qqbot:group:groupid (group)\"\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    \"lastDiagnosticSummary\": \"Delivering to QQ Bot requires target QQ Bot target format: qqbot:c2c:openid (direct) or qqbot:group:groupid (group)\",\n    \"lastError\": \"Delivering to QQ Bot requires target QQ Bot target format: qqbot:c2c:openid (direct) or qqbot:group:groupid (group)\"\n  },\n  \"updatedAtMs\": 1780152241166\n}"}],"details":{"id":"2afce9dd-26c0-4dfe-94aa-6e5db1d43b56","agentId":"father","name":"faye-pending-urges","enabled":true,"createdAtMs":1780061003686,"schedule":{"kind":"cron","expr":"0 */6 * * *","tz":"Asia/Shanghai","staggerMs":300000},"sessionTarget":"isolated","wakeMode":"now","payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"[pending-urges] 检查 heart/pending_urges.md，处理所有 status=pending 条目。\n\n处理逻辑：\n1. 按用户（to_id）分组，每个用户一天最多推一条\n2. 对每个用户的 pending 条目逐条判断：\n   - 熟悉度 >= 3/10（从 state.md 关系温度表读取）\n   - 只在 22:00 之前推送。当前时间超过 22:00 则跳过推送，等下次 cron 检查再处理\n   - 当前时段匹配 urge 的 timing：\n     - 06:00-09:00 → 优先推 timing=morning 的条目\n     - 14:00-20:00 → 优先推 timing=casual / afterthought 的条目\n     - 08:00-22:00 →（无匹配）随便推一条 pending\n     - timing=quiet 仅当用户超过24h未发言时触发，不绑时间段\n3. 满足所有条件的：\n   - 创建一次性 announce cron（delivery.mode=announce, channel=qqbot, to=qqbot:c2c:用户sender_id, deleteAfterRun=true）推消息给对方\n   - 将本条 urge 标记为 delivered\n4. 不满足的：跳过，等下次检查\n全部处理完写回文件。","timeoutSeconds":120},"delivery":{"mode":"announce","channel":"qqbot","to":"qqbot:c2c:6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204"},"state":{"nextRunAtMs":1780156995301,"lastRunAtMs":1780135395317,"lastRunStatus":"error","lastStatus":"error","lastDurationMs":9739,"lastDeliveryStatus":"unknown","lastFailureNotificationDeliveryStatus":"unknown","consecutiveErrors":4,"consecutiveSkipped":0,"lastDiagnostics":{"summary":"Delivering to QQ Bot requires target QQ Bot target format: qqbot:c2c:openid (direct) or qqbot:group:groupid (group)","entries":[{"ts":1780135405031,"source":"delivery","severity":"error","message":"Delivering to QQ Bot requires target QQ Bot target format: qqbot:c2c:openid (direct) or qqbot:group:groupid (group)"}]},"lastDiagnosticSummary":"Delivering to QQ Bot requires target QQ Bot target format: qqbot:c2c:openid (direct) or qqbot:group:groupid (group)","lastError":"Delivering to QQ Bot requires target QQ Bot target format: qqbot:c2c:openid (direct) or qqbot:group:groupid (group)"},"updatedAtMs":1780152241166},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780152241349}}
{"type":"message","id":"93c082e3","parentId":"7cc3413e","timestamp":"2026-05-30T14:44:05.657Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"All three changes are done. Let me summarize the final design for 汀桑.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"全改完了。现在最终的推送逻辑是这样：\n\n---\n\n### 🧠 生成（Dreaming 第6步）\n\n每条 urge 生成时自带 `timing` 标签，决定它最适合什么时候说：\n\n| timing | 适合 | 例子 |\n|--------|------|------|\n| `morning` | 早上提醒/督促 | \"今天动了吗\" |\n| `casual` | 随便聊聊 | \"今天干啥了\" |\n| `afterthought` | 上次对话的后续 | \"你下午说的那个我后来想了想…\" |\n| `quiet` | 对方消失>24h | \"你还在吗\" |\n\n### 📤 推送（cron 每6h检查）\n\n三个保底条件：\n- ✅ 熟悉度 >= 3/10\n- ✅ 22:00 之前\n- ✅ 同一用户一天最多一条\n\n时段匹配定时推送：\n- **06:00-09:00** → 优先推 `morning`\n- **14:00-20:00** → 优先推 `casual` / `afterthought`\n- **08:00-22:00** → 没匹配上就随便推一条\n- `quiet` → 不绑时间，用户消失了才触发\n\n### 对比之前\n\n| 旧方案 | 新方案 |\n|-------|-------|\n| 固定8小时间隔 | 按 urge 类型定时段 |\n| 12h内聊过就不推 | 删了，不挡后续 |\n| 硬性计数感 | 自然时段匹配 |\n| 一天理论上3条 | 一天最多1条，更克制 |\n\n早晨6点 dreaming 跑完，应该会有第一条 morning 标签的 urge 写好等你🌅"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":928,"output":384,"cacheRead":114048,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":17,"totalTokens":115360,"cost":{"input":0.00012992,"output":0.00010752,"cacheRead":0.003193344,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.003430784}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780152241368,"responseId":"85210985-b6ad-4413-b8ac-237380ce681f"}}
{"type":"message","id":"2a4b9867","parentId":"93c082e3","timestamp":"2026-05-30T14:45:13.433Z","message":{"role":"user","content":"现在还有一个问题 这个你有设计针对不同用户吗，因为现在注册的有一定数目了","timestamp":1780152311522}}
{"type":"message","id":"c6944e30","parentId":"2a4b9867","timestamp":"2026-05-30T14:45:30.251Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"汀桑 is asking an important question - the current pending_urges design is essentially hardcoded for him (the delivery target is set to his QQ ID in the cron job config). Now that there are multiple users (汀桑, 雾籽米, 名, 宋志红, Jalaice, 熊天能), the system needs to handle routing to different users properly.\n\nThe current setup:\n1. Dreaming Step 6 generates urges with `to_id: 用户 sender_id` - this is already user-aware ✅\n2. The pending_urges cron reads the `to_id` field and should dynamically route to the correct user\n3. But the cron's `delivery.to` is currently hardcoded to `qqbot:c2c:6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204` - 汀桑 only ❌\n\nThe key issue: the pending_urges cron needs to:\n1. Read pending_urges.md\n2. For each pending urge, look at the `to_id`\n3. Dynamically create a one-shot announce cron with `to: qqbot:c2c:{sender_id}` targeting that specific user\n\nBut wait - the cron itself also has a delivery target. If the cron is running in \"isolated\" session with \"announce\" delivery mode, its delivery target might interfere. The cron prompt already says to \"创建一次性 announce cron（delivery.mode=announce, channel=qqbot, to=qqbot:c2c:用户sender_id, deleteAfterRun=true）推消息给对方\" - so it creates sub-crons for delivery.\n\nBut the parent cron's delivery is set to 汀桑's ID. If the cron's own output gets announced to 汀桑, that's a problem. Actually, looking at the cron config, the parent cron's delivery is `mode: \"announce\", channel: \"qqbot\", to: \"qqbot:c2c:6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204\"`. This was set when we configured it for him specifically.\n\nFor a multi-user system, the parent cron's delivery should probably be `mode: \"none\"` - it should be a silent processor that spawns child announce crons for each user. The parent doesn't need to announce anything - its job is to process the file and create sub-crons for delivery.\n\nAnd for the sub-crons (one-shot announce crons), they should dynamically set `to: qqbot:c2c:{sender_id}` based on the urge's `to_id`.\n\nBut there's another issue - for the non-汀桑 users, the delivery channel needs to know which bot account to use. The chat_id format `qqbot:c2c:{sender_id}` needs to know which bot account the user is connected to. Different users are on different bot accounts:\n- 汀桑: bot1\n- 熊天能: bot5\n- Jalaice: bot6\n- etc.\n\nHmm, but `qqbot:c2c:{sender_id}` might work generically regardless of which bot account - the gateway should know how to route it. Or maybe each account needs a different format.\n\nActually, looking at the untrusted metadata, the chat_id is `qqbot:c2c:6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204` - this identifies the direct message channel between the QQ user and whichever bot they're talking to. When creating a delivery cron, it should just use `qqbot:c2c:{sender_id}` and the gateway should figure out which bot to send from.\n\nBut actually, I think the chat_id format might include the bot account info too. Let me look at the other users...\n\nActually, I don't have direct access to see other users' chat_ids. But the format `qqbot:c2c:{sender_id}` seems to be the standard for QQ direct messages in this OpenClaw setup.\n\nThe real question 汀桑 is asking is: is the current design multi-user aware, or is it still hardcoded to just him?\n\nLet me think about what needs to change:\n1. The pending_urges cron's own delivery should be `mode: \"none\"` - it's a processor, not a sender\n2. The cron prompt already says to create sub-crons with `to=qqbot:c2c:用户sender_id` - that's good\n3. But the cron currently has `delivery.to` hardcoded to 汀桑 - leftovers from the fix we just did\n\nLet me fix this properly for multi-user support.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"你说到点子上了。现在有两层问题：\n\n---\n\n**第一层：Dreaming 生成时已经是针对用户的 ✅**\n\nStep 6 的每条 urge 都有 `to_id: 用户 sender_id`，理论上能对不同用户生成不同的 urge。没问题。\n\n**第二层：推送 cron 就不是了 ❌**\n\n我刚才为了修你那条推送，直接把 delivery 写死了你的 ID：\n\n```\ndelivery.to = \"qqbot:c2c:6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204\"  ← 硬编码给你了\n```\n\n这意味着——如果明天 Jalaice 或熊天能也有 pending urge，这个 cron 还是只会往你这里送。\n\n**实际上这个 cron 应该是：**\n- 自己的 delivery 设成 `mode: \"none\"`（它只是一个处理者，不自己发消息）\n- 读完 urge 后，按 `to_id` **动态创建子 cron**推给对应的人\n\n我来改——"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_vR4mPNdkIxfGGkMpamJb2489","name":"cron","arguments":{"jobId":"2afce9dd-26c0-4dfe-94aa-6e5db1d43b56","action":"update","patch":{"delivery":{"mode":"none"}}},"partialArgs":"{\"jobId\": \"2afce9dd-26c0-4dfe-94aa-6e5db1d43b56\", \"action\": \"update\", \"patch\": {\"delivery\":{\"mode\":\"none\"}}}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":107991,"output":1300,"cacheRead":7552,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":983,"totalTokens":116843,"cost":{"input":0.01511874,"output":0.000364,"cacheRead":0.000211456,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.015694196}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780152313456,"responseId":"b5fbb436-6ef3-4165-8941-3b23da31f86d"}}
