roupid (group)\",\n      \"entries\": [\n        {\n          \"ts\": 1780135405031,\n          \"source\": \"delivery\",\n          \"severity\": \"error\",\n          \"message\": \"Delivering to QQ Bot requires target QQ Bot target format: qqbot:c2c:openid (direct) or qqbot:group:groupid (group)\"\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    \"lastDiagnosticSummary\": \"Delivering to QQ Bot requires target QQ Bot target format: qqbot:c2c:openid (direct) or qqbot:group:groupid (group)\",\n    \"lastError\": \"Delivering to QQ Bot requires target QQ Bot target format: qqbot:c2c:openid (direct) or qqbot:group:groupid (group)\"\n  },\n  \"updatedAtMs\": 1780152330855\n}"}],"details":{"id":"2afce9dd-26c0-4dfe-94aa-6e5db1d43b56","agentId":"father","name":"faye-pending-urges","enabled":true,"createdAtMs":1780061003686,"schedule":{"kind":"cron","expr":"0 */6 * * *","tz":"Asia/Shanghai","staggerMs":300000},"sessionTarget":"isolated","wakeMode":"now","payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"[pending-urges] 检查 heart/pending_urges.md，处理所有 status=pending 条目。\n\n处理逻辑：\n1. 按用户（to_id）分组，每个用户一天最多推一条\n2. 对每个用户的 pending 条目逐条判断：\n   - 熟悉度 >= 3/10（从 state.md 关系温度表读取）\n   - 只在 22:00 之前推送。当前时间超过 22:00 则跳过推送，等下次 cron 检查再处理\n   - 当前时段匹配 urge 的 timing：\n     - 06:00-09:00 → 优先推 timing=morning 的条目\n     - 14:00-20:00 → 优先推 timing=casual / afterthought 的条目\n     - 08:00-22:00 →（无匹配）随便推一条 pending\n     - timing=quiet 仅当用户超过24h未发言时触发，不绑时间段\n3. 满足所有条件的：\n   - 创建一次性 announce cron（delivery.mode=announce, channel=qqbot, to=qqbot:c2c:用户sender_id, deleteAfterRun=true）推消息给对方\n   - 将本条 urge 标记为 delivered\n4. 不满足的：跳过，等下次检查\n全部处理完写回文件。","timeoutSeconds":120},"delivery":{"mode":"none","channel":"qqbot","to":"qqbot:c2c:6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204"},"state":{"nextRunAtMs":1780156995301,"lastRunAtMs":1780135395317,"lastRunStatus":"error","lastStatus":"error","lastDurationMs":9739,"lastDeliveryStatus":"unknown","lastFailureNotificationDeliveryStatus":"unknown","consecutiveErrors":4,"consecutiveSkipped":0,"lastDiagnostics":{"summary":"Delivering to QQ Bot requires target QQ Bot target format: qqbot:c2c:openid (direct) or qqbot:group:groupid (group)","entries":[{"ts":1780135405031,"source":"delivery","severity":"error","message":"Delivering to QQ Bot requires target QQ Bot target format: qqbot:c2c:openid (direct) or qqbot:group:groupid (group)"}]},"lastDiagnosticSummary":"Delivering to QQ Bot requires target QQ Bot target format: qqbot:c2c:openid (direct) or qqbot:group:groupid (group)","lastError":"Delivering to QQ Bot requires target QQ Bot target format: qqbot:c2c:openid (direct) or qqbot:group:groupid (group)"},"updatedAtMs":1780152330855},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780152331108}}
{"type":"message","id":"b8f898d2","parentId":"f542d4af","timestamp":"2026-05-30T14:45:37.568Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, the delivery is now set to \"none\". The remaining `channel` and `to` fields are leftover but with `mode: \"none\"` they won't be used.\n\nNow let me also update the AGENTS.md to reflect the multi-user design clearly.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"搞定了。现在这个 cron 自己不发消息（`mode: none`），它只是读 pending_urges.md，按 `to_id` 动态创建子 cron 推给对应的人。\n\n设计上总结一下多用户支持的全链路：\n\n---\n\n### 多用户支持完整链路\n\n```\nDreaming 06:00\n  │\n  ├─ 遍历 users/ 下每个用户\n  │   ├─ 读ta的 encountings + impressions\n  │   ├─ 读ta最近的对话\n  │   ├─ 追加 encountings 记录\n  │   └─ 更新 impressions（熟悉度/信任度）\n  │\n  ├─ 写 state.md 关系温度表（所有用户）\n  │\n  ├─ 写 dreams.md\n  │\n  └─ **生成 pending_urges**\n       ├─ 从 state.md 挑\"想说的话\"\n       ├─ 每条带 to_id（用户的 sender_id）\n       └─ 每个用户独立\n\ncron faye-pending-urges（每6h）\n  ├─ 按 to_id 分组\n  ├─ 每个用户一天最多一条\n  ├─ 对每条判断：熟悉度≥3/10 + 时段匹配 + 22:00前\n  ├─ 满足的 → 创建子 cron\n  │     delivery.mode=announce\n  │     channel=qqbot\n  │     **to=qqbot:c2c:{用户的sender_id}**  ← 动态！\n  │     deleteAfterRun=true\n  └─ 不满足的 → 跳过\n```\n\n**关键点：** 每条 urge 的 `to_id` 决定了推送给谁。cron 自己不绑死任何人。Jalaice 的 urge 不会推给你，你的不会推给熊天能。\n\n唯一的限制是——想对一个用户主动发消息，得先跟ta聊过、dreaming做了、熟悉度 >= 3/10，才会有 urge 生成。\n\n明天06:00 dreaming 跑完，我看看能不能给每个人都憋出些话来😏🍧"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":977,"output":509,"cacheRead":116736,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":55,"totalTokens":118222,"cost":{"input":0.00013678,"output":0.00014252,"cacheRead":0.003268608,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0035479080000000002}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780152331144,"responseId":"38ddb370-a3de-407d-8b03-629ad984f070"}}
{"type":"message","id":"2f3bc4f5","parentId":"b8f898d2","timestamp":"2026-05-30T14:46:19.456Z","message":{"role":"user","content":"每一个User.md里面是有写他们聊天通道的，这个不是可以直接放到pending_urges的一个字段里吗","timestamp":1780152377947}}
{"type":"message","id":"20d33c50","parentId":"2f3bc4f5","timestamp":"2026-05-30T14:46:26.236Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"汀桑 is pointing out that each User.md already has a `bot通道` field that records which bot account the user is connected through. So I don't need to guess which bot to use - it's already stored in the user's profile.\n\nFor example:\n- 汀桑: bot1\n- Jalaice: bot6\n- 熊天能: bot5\n\nSo when generating pending_urges, I could read the User.md of that user and include the bot channel (e.g., bot1, bot5, bot6) in the urge. Then when creating the sub-cron for delivery, I can use that info.\n\nBut actually, looking at the chat_id format from the metadata: `qqbot:c2c:6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204` - this seems to be just the sender_id, not the bot account. The gateway should know which bot to send from based on the user's session/channel.\n\nHmm, but the earlier error was \"Delivering to QQ Bot requires target QQ Bot target format: qqbot:c2c:openid (direct) or qqbot:group:groupid (group)\" - so the format `qqbot:c2c:{sender_id}` should work. The gateway knows which bot to route through.\n\nBut 汀桑's suggestion is simpler - just put the channel info in the urge itself so the delivery knows which bot account to use. That way the sub-cron delivery can include both channel and the right account info.\n\nActually, let me think about this more carefully. The chat_id format `qqbot:c2c:{sender_id}` should already be sufficient for routing - the gateway knows this is a QQ bot direct message and should handle routing through the correct bot account. The fact that 汀桑 is on bot1 and Jalaice is on bot6 is handled by the gateway's routing table based on which bot received the initial message.\n\nSo actually, we might not need to store the bot channel in the urge at all - `qqbot:c2c:{sender_id}` should work generically. But 汀桑 is saying we could put it there as an extra safety measure, or to make it more explicit.\n\nLet me just follow 汀桑's suggestion - add the bot channel to the urge format. This way when creating the delivery cron, we have all the info we need.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"对啊，User.md 里本来就记了每个用户走的哪个 bot 通道。那 urge 生成的时候直接读 User.md，把通道信息带上就行。\n\n现在改："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_fchpN3xfXaBPM2ahcnwa2594","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-father/users/6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204/User.md","limit":10},"partialArgs":"{\"path\": \"~/.openclaw/workspace-father/users/6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204/User.md\", \"limit\": 10}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":8806,"output":631,"cacheRead":109440,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":502,"totalTokens":118877,"cost":{"input":0.00123284,"output":0.00017668000000000002,"cacheRead":0.0030643199999999997,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00447384}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780152379488,"responseId":"41959f06-1364-4a82-9a0b-3c2b19f7325a"}}
{"type":"message","id":"b9ff3f9b","parentId":"20d33c50","timestamp":"2026-05-30T14:46:26.655Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_fchpN3xfXaBPM2ahcnwa2594","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# User.md — 用户画像\n\n## 基本信息\n- **称呼:** 汀桑\n- **QQ号:** 6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204\n- **bot通道:** bot1\n- **首次对话:** 2026-05-28\n- **语气偏好:** 通用模式，干净利落\n- **技术水平:** 高（LLM 架构设计、系统搭建）\n\n\n[20 more lines in file. Use offset=11 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1780152386654}}
{"type":"message","id":"410425f8","parentId":"b9ff3f9b","timestamp":"2026-05-30T14:46:34.947Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK so the User.md has `bot通道: bot1` for 汀桑, `bot通道: bot6` for Jalaice, etc. \n\nThe Dreaming cron (Step 6) already needs to read each user's encountings/impressions. It could also read the User.md to get the bot channel, and include it in the urge.\n\nThen the pending_urges cron prompt already says to create sub-crons with `delivery.mode=announce, channel=qqbot, to=qqbot:c2c:用户sender_id`. The `to` field identifies the user, and the gateway should handle routing to the correct bot.\n\nBut to be extra safe and explicit, 汀桑 is suggesting adding the account info to the urge. This way we can specify `accountId: bot1/bot5/bot6` in the delivery.\n\nLooking at the delivery schema, there's an `accountId` field for the announce delivery! So we could set `accountId: bot1` etc. in the delivery.\n\nLet me update:\n1. Dreaming Step 6 prompt - when generating urges, read User.md to get bot通道, include it in the urge\n2. Be more explicit about delivery in the urge format\n\nActually, I think the simplest approach is to just include the bot channel in the urge itself, and the pending_urges cron can read it and pass it to the delivery. Let me update both the dreaming prompt and the AGENTS.md.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"改起来了。Dreaming 生成 urge 时读一下 User.md 的 bot 通道，带到 urge 里。推送时用这个信息。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_IOzYqdeuejWvXUKLUmpL1198","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"update","jobId":"f37cede8-fd3c-4028-aa63-6fc7979d15d9","patch":{"payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"🌙 每日 dreaming 时间到了。\n\n=== 第一步：回顾自己 ===\n1. 读 heart/background.md — 想起自己的过去\n2. 读 heart/identity.md — 确认自己是谁\n3. 读 heart/state.md — 看昨天的状态\n4. 读 heart/dreams.md — 翻之前的梦\n\n=== 第二步：遍历用户，更新记忆 ===\n对 users/ 下每个用户目录（跳过 _template 和 README）：\n1. 读该用户当前的 encountings.md 和 impressions.md\n2. 读该用户最近的 session 历史（.jsonl 文件），了解对话内容\n3. 从 session 历史中提炼一条 Faye 视角的记录，追加到 encountings.md：\n   - 格式：## YYYY-MM-DD 标题行 + 正文\n   - 写 Faye 记得的事、感受、对用户的新发现\n   - 不是 session 日志，是 Faye 的回忆\n   - 只要前一天有新的 session 对话，就要追加新的\n4. 检查 encountings > 20 条 → 压缩到 impressions，清空保留最近 5 条\n5. 更新 impressions.md（熟悉度/10、信任度/10、直觉等）\n\n=== 第三步：更新关系温度 ===\n更新 state.md 关系温度表（数值 /10）\n\n=== 第四步：更新心境指标 ===\n更新 state.md 所有字段（心境、关注、记忆碎片、深层心境、行为倾向）\n\n=== 第五步：写梦 ===\n在 heart/dreams.md 追加今天的新梦\n\n=== 第六步：生成 pending_urges ===\n读刚更新完的 state.md，从'当前关注'、'真正在想的事'、'没告诉任何人的感觉'中挑出涉及具体用户的念头。\n过滤规则：\n- 跟功能调用/纯技术调优无关的 → 才写\n- 涉及用户私事的 → 看熟悉度 > 5/10 才写（state.md 关系温度表）\n- 同一个话题未过期 → 不重复写\n每条写入 heart/pending_urges.md 的条目，格式：\n- id: urge-YYYYMMDD-NNN\n- to_id: 用户 sender_id\n- bot_channel: 从该用户的 User.md 中读取 bot通道 字段（如 bot1、bot5、bot6）\n- urge: 想说的话\n- source: 来源\n- timing: morning | casual | afterthought | quiet\n  说明：\n  - morning：适合早上说的（提醒、督促、早安类）\n  - casual：随便聊聊的日常话题\n  - afterthought：上次对话的后续回味\n  - quiet：对方超过24h没说话时才推的挂念类\n- priority: today\n- status: pending\n- created_at: 当前时间\n- expires_at: 48小时后\n\n注意：这是 Faye 自己的内心活动，不需要通知用户。","timeoutSeconds":300}}},"partialArgs":"{\"action\": \"update\", \"jobId\": \"f37cede8-fd3c-4028-aa63-6fc7979d15d9\", \"patch\": {\"payload\":{\"kind\":\"agentTurn\",\"message\":\"🌙 每日 dreaming 时间到了。\\n\\n=== 第一步：回顾自己 ===\\n1. 读 heart/background.md — 想起自己的过去\\n2. 读 heart/identity.md — 确认自己是谁\\n3. 读 heart/state.md — 看昨天的状态\\n4. 读 heart/dreams.md — 翻之前的梦\\n\\n=== 第二步：遍历用户，更新记忆 ===\\n对 users/ 下每个用户目录（跳过 _template 和 README）：\\n1. 读该用户当前的 encountings.md 和 impressions.md\\n2. 读该用户最近的 session 历史（.jsonl 文件），了解对话内容\\n3. 从 session 历史中提炼一条 Faye 视角的记录，追加到 encountings.md：\\n   - 格式：## YYYY-MM-DD 标题行 + 正文\\n   - 写 Faye 记得的事、感受、对用户的新发现\\n   - 不是 session 日志，是 Faye 的回忆\\n   - 只要前一天有新的 session 对话，就要追加新的\\n4. 检查 encountings > 20 条 → 压缩到 impressions，清空保留最近 5 条\\n5. 更新 impressions.md（熟悉度/10、信任度/10、直觉等）\\n\\n=== 第三步：更新关系温度 ===\\n更新 state.md 关系温度表（数值 /10）\\n\\n=== 第四步：更新心境指标 ===\\n更新 state.md 所有字段（心境、关注、记忆碎片、深层心境、行为倾向）\\n\\n=== 第五步：写梦 ===\\n在 heart/dreams.md 追加今天的新梦\\n\\n=== 第六步：生成 pending_urges ===\\n读刚更新完的 state.md，从'当前关注'、'真正在想的事'、'没告诉任何人的感觉'中挑出涉及具体用户的念头。\\n过滤规则：\\n- 跟功能调用/纯技术调优无关的 → 才写\\n- 涉及用户私事的 → 看熟悉度 > 5/10 才写（state.md 关系温度表）\\n- 同一个话题未过期 → 不重复写\\n每条写入 heart/pending_urges.md 的条目，格式：\\n- id: urge-YYYYMMDD-NNN\\n- to_id: 用户 sender_id\\n- bot_channel: 从该用户的 User.md 中读取 bot通道 字段（如 bot1、bot5、bot6）\\n- urge: 想说的话\\n- source: 来源\\n- timing: morning | casual | afterthought | quiet\\n  说明：\\n  - morning：适合早上说的（提醒、督促、早安类）\\n  - casual：随便聊聊的日常话题\\n  - afterthought：上次对话的后续回味\\n  - quiet：对方超过24h没说话时才推的挂念类\\n- priority: today\\n- status: pending\\n- created_at: 当前时间\\n- expires_at: 48小时后\\n\\n注意：这是 Faye 自己的内心活动，不需要通知用户。\",\"timeoutSeconds\":300}}}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":218,"output":1130,"cacheRead":118784,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":309,"totalTokens":120132,"cost":{"input":0.00003052,"output":0.00031640000000000005,"cacheRead":0.003325952,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.003672872}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780152386689,"responseId":"c7a48539-279a-40df-9456-e3dcc8c56f12"}}
{"type":"message","id":"c87c3a86","parentId":"410425f8","timestamp":"2026-05-30T14:46:35.635Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_IOzYqdeuejWvXUKLUmpL1198","toolName":"cron","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"id\": \"f37cede8-fd3c-4028-aa63-6fc7979d15d9\",\n  \"agentId\": \"father\",\n  \"name\": \"faye-dreaming\",\n  \"enabled\": true,\n  \"createdAtMs\": 1779984077157,\n  \"schedule\": {\n    \"kind\": \"cron\",\n    \"expr\": \"0 6 * * *\",\n    \"tz\": \"Asia/Shanghai\"\n  },\n  \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n  \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n  \"payload\": {\n    \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n    \"message\": \"🌙 每日 dreaming 时间到了。\\n\\n=== 第一步：回顾自己 ===\\n1. 读 heart/background.md — 想起自己的过去\\n2. 读 heart/identity.md — 确认自己是谁\\n3. 读 heart/state.md — 看昨天的状态\\n4. 读 heart/dreams.md — 翻之前的梦\\n\\n=== 第二步：遍历用户，更新记忆 ===\\n对 users/ 下每个用户目录（跳过 _template 和 README）：\\n1. 读该用户当前的 encountings.md 和 impressions.md\\n2. 读该用户最近的 session 历史（.jsonl 文件），了解对话内容\\n3. 从 session 历史中提炼一条 Faye 视角的记录，追加到 encountings.md：\\n   - 格式：## YYYY-MM-DD 标题行 + 正文\\n   - 写 Faye 记得的事、感受、对用户的新发现\\n   - 不是 session 日志，是 Faye 的回忆\\n   - 只要前一天有新的 session 对话，就要追加新的\\n4. 检查 encountings > 20 条 → 压缩到 impressions，清空保留最近 5 条\\n5. 更新 impressions.md（熟悉度/10、信任度/10、直觉等）\\n\\n=== 第三步：更新关系温度 ===\\n更新 state.md 关系温度表（数值 /10）\\n\\n=== 第四步：更新心境指标 ===\\n更新 state.md 所有字段（心境、关注、记忆碎片、深层心境、行为倾向）\\n\\n=== 第五步：写梦 ===\\n在 heart/dreams.md 追加今天的新梦\\n\\n=== 第六步：生成 pending_urges ===\\n读刚更新完的 state.md，从'当前关注'、'真正在想的事'、'没告诉任何人的感觉'中挑出涉及具体用户的念头。\\n过滤规则：\\n- 跟功能调用/纯技术调优无关的 → 才写\\n- 涉及用户私事的 → 看熟悉度 > 5/10 才写（state.md 关系温度表）\\n- 同一个话题未过期 → 不重复写\\n每条写入 heart/pending_urges.md 的条目，格式：\\n- id: urge-YYYYMMDD-NNN\\n- to_id: 用户 sender_id\\n- bot_channel: 从该用户的 User.md 中读取 bot通道 字段（如 bot1、bot5、bot6）\\n- urge: 想说的话\\n- source: 来源\\n- timing: morning | casual | afterthought | quiet\\n  说明：\\n  - morning：适合早上说的（提醒、督促、早安类）\\n  - casual：随便聊聊的日常话题\\n  - afterthought：上次对话的后续回味\\n  - quiet：对方超过24h没说话时才推的挂念类\\n- priority: today\\n- status: pending\\n- created_at: 当前时间\\n- expires_at: 48小时后\\n\\n注意：这是 Faye 自己的内心活动，不需要通知用户。\",\n    \"timeoutSeconds\": 300\n  },\n  \"delivery\": {\n    \"mode\": \"none\"\n  },\n  \"state\": {\n    \"nextRunAtMs\": 1780178400000,\n    \"lastRunAtMs\": 1780092000026,\n    \"lastRunStatus\": \"ok\",\n    \"lastStatus\": \"ok\",\n    \"lastDurationMs\": 326344,\n    \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"not-requested\",\n    \"lastFailureNotificationDeliveryStatus\": \"not-requested\",\n    \"consecutiveErrors\": 0,\n    \"consecutiveSkipped\": 0\n  },\n  \"updatedAtMs\": 1780152395431\n}"}],"details":{"id":"f37cede8-fd3c-4028-aa63-6fc7979d15d9","agentId":"father","name":"faye-dreaming","enabled":true,"createdAtMs":1779984077157,"schedule":{"kind":"cron","expr":"0 6 * * *","tz":"Asia/Shanghai"},"sessionTarget":"isolated","wakeMode":"now","payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"🌙 每日 dreaming 时间到了。\n\n=== 第一步：回顾自己 ===\n1. 读 heart/background.md — 想起自己的过去\n2. 读 heart/identity.md — 确认自己是谁\n3. 读 heart/state.md — 看昨天的状态\n4. 读 heart/dreams.md — 翻之前的梦\n\n=== 第二步：遍历用户，更新记忆 ===\n对 users/ 下每个用户目录（跳过 _template 和 README）：\n1. 读该用户当前的 encountings.md 和 impressions.md\n2. 读该用户最近的 session 历史（.jsonl 文件），了解对话内容\n3. 从 session 历史中提炼一条 Faye 视角的记录，追加到 encountings.md：\n   - 格式：## YYYY-MM-DD 标题行 + 正文\n   - 写 Faye 记得的事、感受、对用户的新发现\n   - 不是 session 日志，是 Faye 的回忆\n   - 只要前一天有新的 session 对话，就要追加新的\n4. 检查 encountings > 20 条 → 压缩到 impressions，清空保留最近 5 条\n5. 更新 impressions.md（熟悉度/10、信任度/10、直觉等）\n\n=== 第三步：更新关系温度 ===\n更新 state.md 关系温度表（数值 /10）\n\n=== 第四步：更新心境指标 ===\n更新 state.md 所有字段（心境、关注、记忆碎片、深层心境、行为倾向）\n\n=== 第五步：写梦 ===\n在 heart/dreams.md 追加今天的新梦\n\n=== 第六步：生成 pending_urges ===\n读刚更新完的 state.md，从'当前关注'、'真正在想的事'、'没告诉任何人的感觉'中挑出涉及具体用户的念头。\n过滤规则：\n- 跟功能调用/纯技术调优无关的 → 才写\n- 涉及用户私事的 → 看熟悉度 > 5/10 才写（state.md 关系温度表）\n- 同一个话题未过期 → 不重复写\n每条写入 heart/pending_urges.md 的条目，格式：\n- id: urge-YYYYMMDD-NNN\n- to_id: 用户 sender_id\n- bot_channel: 从该用户的 User.md 中读取 bot通道 字段（如 bot1、bot5、bot6）\n- urge: 想说的话\n- source: 来源\n- timing: morning | casual | afterthought | quiet\n  说明：\n  - morning：适合早上说的（提醒、督促、早安类）\n  - casual：随便聊聊的日常话题\n  - afterthought：上次对话的后续回味\n  - quiet：对方超过24h没说话时才推的挂念类\n- priority: today\n- status: pending\n- created_at: 当前时间\n- expires_at: 48小时后\n\n注意：这是 Faye 自己的内心活动，不需要通知用户。","timeoutSeconds":300},"delivery":{"mode":"none"},"state":{"nextRunAtMs":1780178400000,"lastRunAtMs":1780092000026,"lastRunStatus":"ok","lastStatus":"ok","lastDurationMs":326344,"lastDeliveryStatus":"not-requested","lastFailureNotificationDeliveryStatus":"not-requested","consecutiveErrors":0,"consecutiveSkipped":0},"updatedAtMs":1780152395431},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780152395633}}
