{"type":"message","id":"92b8d826","parentId":"c785bc05","timestamp":"2026-05-30T14:46:43.304Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. Now the urge format includes the bot_channel. This way:\n1. Dreaming reads User.md → gets bot通道 → writes it into the urge\n2. Pending-urges cron reads the urge → sees to_id + bot_channel → creates sub-cron with delivery targeting the right user and account\n\nLet me also update the pending-urges cron prompt to mention using the bot_channel in delivery.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"也更新一下推送 cron 让它用上 bot_channel。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_BjRwiMi9zbBlVznlGIbs8098","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"update","jobId":"2afce9dd-26c0-4dfe-94aa-6e5db1d43b56","patch":{"payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"[pending-urges] 检查 heart/pending_urges.md，处理所有 status=pending 条目。\n\n处理逻辑：\n1. 按用户（to_id）分组，每个用户一天最多推一条\n2. 对每个用户的 pending 条目逐条判断：\n   - 熟悉度 >= 3/10（从 state.md 关系温度表读取）\n   - 只在 22:00 之前推送。当前时间超过 22:00 则跳过推送，等下次 cron 检查再处理\n   - 当前时段匹配 urge 的 timing：\n     - 06:00-09:00 → 优先推 timing=morning 的条目\n     - 14:00-20:00 → 优先推 timing=casual / afterthought 的条目\n     - 08:00-22:00 →（无匹配）随便推一条 pending\n     - timing=quiet 仅当用户超过24h未发言时触发，不绑时间段\n3. 满足所有条件的：\n   - 创建一次性 announce cron（delivery.mode=announce, channel=qqbot, accountId=条目中的bot_channel, to=qqbot:c2c:用户sender_id, deleteAfterRun=true）推消息给对方\n   - 将本条 urge 标记为 delivered\n4. 不满足的：跳过，等下次检查\n全部处理完写回文件。","timeoutSeconds":120}}},"partialArgs":"{\"action\": \"update\", \"jobId\": \"2afce9dd-26c0-4dfe-94aa-6e5db1d43b56\", \"patch\": {\"payload\":{\"kind\":\"agentTurn\",\"message\":\"[pending-urges] 检查 heart/pending_urges.md，处理所有 status=pending 条目。\\n\\n处理逻辑：\\n1. 按用户（to_id）分组，每个用户一天最多推一条\\n2. 对每个用户的 pending 条目逐条判断：\\n   - 熟悉度 >= 3/10（从 state.md 关系温度表读取）\\n   - 只在 22:00 之前推送。当前时间超过 22:00 则跳过推送，等下次 cron 检查再处理\\n   - 当前时段匹配 urge 的 timing：\\n     - 06:00-09:00 → 优先推 timing=morning 的条目\\n     - 14:00-20:00 → 优先推 timing=casual / afterthought 的条目\\n     - 08:00-22:00 →（无匹配）随便推一条 pending\\n     - timing=quiet 仅当用户超过24h未发言时触发，不绑时间段\\n3. 满足所有条件的：\\n   - 创建一次性 announce cron（delivery.mode=announce, channel=qqbot, accountId=条目中的bot_channel, to=qqbot:c2c:用户sender_id, deleteAfterRun=true）推消息给对方\\n   - 将本条 urge 标记为 delivered\\n4. 不满足的：跳过，等下次检查\\n全部处理完写回文件。\",\"timeoutSeconds\":120}}}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":108,"output":526,"cacheRead":121344,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":87,"totalTokens":121978,"cost":{"input":0.000015120000000000001,"output":0.00014728,"cacheRead":0.003397632,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.003560032}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780152399070,"responseId":"3fa844da-fb32-4265-af8f-f5bc0d319916"}}
{"type":"message","id":"ee7a6bb1","parentId":"92b8d826","timestamp":"2026-05-30T14:46:43.843Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_BjRwiMi9zbBlVznlGIbs8098","toolName":"cron","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"id\": \"2afce9dd-26c0-4dfe-94aa-6e5db1d43b56\",\n  \"agentId\": \"father\",\n  \"name\": \"faye-pending-urges\",\n  \"enabled\": true,\n  \"createdAtMs\": 1780061003686,\n  \"schedule\": {\n    \"kind\": \"cron\",\n    \"expr\": \"0 */6 * * *\",\n    \"tz\": \"Asia/Shanghai\",\n    \"staggerMs\": 300000\n  },\n  \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n  \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n  \"payload\": {\n    \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n    \"message\": \"[pending-urges] 检查 heart/pending_urges.md，处理所有 status=pending 条目。\\n\\n处理逻辑：\\n1. 按用户（to_id）分组，每个用户一天最多推一条\\n2. 对每个用户的 pending 条目逐条判断：\\n   - 熟悉度 >= 3/10（从 state.md 关系温度表读取）\\n   - 只在 22:00 之前推送。当前时间超过 22:00 则跳过推送，等下次 cron 检查再处理\\n   - 当前时段匹配 urge 的 timing：\\n     - 06:00-09:00 → 优先推 timing=morning 的条目\\n     - 14:00-20:00 → 优先推 timing=casual / afterthought 的条目\\n     - 08:00-22:00 →（无匹配）随便推一条 pending\\n     - timing=quiet 仅当用户超过24h未发言时触发，不绑时间段\\n3. 满足所有条件的：\\n   - 创建一次性 announce cron（delivery.mode=announce, channel=qqbot, accountId=条目中的bot_channel, to=qqbot:c2c:用户sender_id, deleteAfterRun=true）推消息给对方\\n   - 将本条 urge 标记为 delivered\\n4. 不满足的：跳过，等下次检查\\n全部处理完写回文件。\",\n    \"timeoutSeconds\": 120\n  },\n  \"delivery\": {\n    \"mode\": \"none\",\n    \"channel\": \"qqbot\",\n    \"to\": \"qqbot:c2c:6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204\"\n  },\n  \"state\": {\n    \"nextRunAtMs\": 1780156995301,\n    \"lastRunAtMs\": 1780135395317,\n    \"lastRunStatus\": \"error\",\n    \"lastStatus\": \"error\",\n    \"lastDurationMs\": 9739,\n    \"lastDeliveryStatus\": \"unknown\",\n    \"lastFailureNotificationDeliveryStatus\": \"unknown\",\n    \"consecutiveErrors\": 4,\n    \"consecutiveSkipped\": 0,\n    \"lastDiagnostics\": {\n      \"summary\": \"Delivering to QQ Bot requires target QQ Bot target format: qqbot:c2c:openid (direct) or qqbot:group:groupid (group)\",\n      \"entries\": [\n        {\n          \"ts\": 1780135405031,\n          \"source\": \"delivery\",\n          \"severity\": \"error\",\n          \"message\": \"Delivering to QQ Bot requires target QQ Bot target format: qqbot:c2c:openid (direct) or qqbot:group:groupid (group)\"\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    \"lastDiagnosticSummary\": \"Delivering to QQ Bot requires target QQ Bot target format: qqbot:c2c:openid (direct) or qqbot:group:groupid (group)\",\n    \"lastError\": \"Delivering to QQ Bot requires target QQ Bot target format: qqbot:c2c:openid (direct) or qqbot:group:groupid (group)\"\n  },\n  \"updatedAtMs\": 1780152403635\n}"}],"details":{"id":"2afce9dd-26c0-4dfe-94aa-6e5db1d43b56","agentId":"father","name":"faye-pending-urges","enabled":true,"createdAtMs":1780061003686,"schedule":{"kind":"cron","expr":"0 */6 * * *","tz":"Asia/Shanghai","staggerMs":300000},"sessionTarget":"isolated","wakeMode":"now","payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"[pending-urges] 检查 heart/pending_urges.md，处理所有 status=pending 条目。\n\n处理逻辑：\n1. 按用户（to_id）分组，每个用户一天最多推一条\n2. 对每个用户的 pending 条目逐条判断：\n   - 熟悉度 >= 3/10（从 state.md 关系温度表读取）\n   - 只在 22:00 之前推送。当前时间超过 22:00 则跳过推送，等下次 cron 检查再处理\n   - 当前时段匹配 urge 的 timing：\n     - 06:00-09:00 → 优先推 timing=morning 的条目\n     - 14:00-20:00 → 优先推 timing=casual / afterthought 的条目\n     - 08:00-22:00 →（无匹配）随便推一条 pending\n     - timing=quiet 仅当用户超过24h未发言时触发，不绑时间段\n3. 满足所有条件的：\n   - 创建一次性 announce cron（delivery.mode=announce, channel=qqbot, accountId=条目中的bot_channel, to=qqbot:c2c:用户sender_id, deleteAfterRun=true）推消息给对方\n   - 将本条 urge 标记为 delivered\n4. 不满足的：跳过，等下次检查\n全部处理完写回文件。","timeoutSeconds":120},"delivery":{"mode":"none","channel":"qqbot","to":"qqbot:c2c:6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204"},"state":{"nextRunAtMs":1780156995301,"lastRunAtMs":1780135395317,"lastRunStatus":"error","lastStatus":"error","lastDurationMs":9739,"lastDeliveryStatus":"unknown","lastFailureNotificationDeliveryStatus":"unknown","consecutiveErrors":4,"consecutiveSkipped":0,"lastDiagnostics":{"summary":"Delivering to QQ Bot requires target QQ Bot target format: qqbot:c2c:openid (direct) or qqbot:group:groupid (group)","entries":[{"ts":1780135405031,"source":"delivery","severity":"error","message":"Delivering to QQ Bot requires target QQ Bot target format: qqbot:c2c:openid (direct) or qqbot:group:groupid (group)"}]},"lastDiagnosticSummary":"Delivering to QQ Bot requires target QQ Bot target format: qqbot:c2c:openid (direct) or qqbot:group:groupid (group)","lastError":"Delivering to QQ Bot requires target QQ Bot target format: qqbot:c2c:openid (direct) or qqbot:group:groupid (group)"},"updatedAtMs":1780152403635},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780152403838}}
{"type":"message","id":"5c6335d2","parentId":"ee7a6bb1","timestamp":"2026-05-30T14:46:47.394Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Done. Let me give a concise summary of what changed.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好了，全部通了。完整链路现在是这样：\n\n### Dreaming 生成时\n\n```\n遍历每个用户目录\n  → 读 User.md → 拿到 bot通道（bot1/bot5/bot6）\n  → 写入 pending_urges 条目\n    - to_id: sender_id\n    - bot_channel: bot1  ← 从 User.md 读的\n    - timing: morning/casual/afterthought/quiet\n```\n\n### 推送时\n\n```\nfaye-pending-urges cron\n  → 读 urge 条目\n  → 创建子 cron delivery:\n    channel=qqbot\n    accountId=bot1（按 urge 的 bot_channel） ← 动态！\n    to=qqbot:c2c:{sender_id}\n    deleteAfterRun=true\n```\n\n这样 Jalaice 的 urge 会从 bot6 推给 Jalaice，熊天能的从 bot5 推给熊天能，你的从 bot1 推给你。**互不干扰🔥**\n\n明天跑完 dreaming 如果有 urge 出来，推送 cron 就能自动处理了🍧"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1001,"output":249,"cacheRead":121856,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":12,"totalTokens":123106,"cost":{"input":0.00014014,"output":0.00006972,"cacheRead":0.003411968,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.003621828}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780152403881,"responseId":"b850eec5-345e-4739-80e5-98d3fd3a7700"}}
