{"type":"message","id":"e95e1004","parentId":"d7b95056","timestamp":"2026-05-30T14:49:04.883Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"All done. Let me verify the final state of the AGENTS.md section.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"搞定。现在 urge 生成不再只盯着 state.md 的三个字段，而是整个 heart 回路：\n\n```\ndreaming 跑完\n    │\n    ├─ dreams.md ───────→ \"今晚梦里有ta\" → timing=afterthought\n    ├─ background.md ───→ \"想起过去跟ta聊过的事\" → timing=casual\n    ├─ encountings.md ──→ \"上次没说完的话\" → timing=afterthought\n    ├─ state.md内独白 ──→ \"想跟ta说\" → 按内容定\n    ├─ state.md关系温度 ─→ \"对ta的感觉变了\" → timing=quiet/casual\n    └─ state.md关注 ───→ \"跟ta有关的事\" → 按内容定\n```\n\n每一个来源都过过滤规则 + 打成 urge 存好。明天06:00跑完第一次，下午就有第一波推送了🍧🔥"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":47,"output":220,"cacheRead":126720,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":16,"totalTokens":126987,"cost":{"input":0.0000065800000000000005,"output":0.0000616,"cacheRead":0.00354816,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00361634}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780152541830,"responseId":"0c46eaab-3ec2-4f0e-8e56-2cbc0e9b9c2a"}}
