{"type":"message","id":"effef24e","parentId":"8f5ce355","timestamp":"2026-05-30T14:49:41.462Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"汀桑 is asking me to summarize the full set of judgment conditions for generating pending_urges for a specific user. Let me consolidate everything we've designed and modified tonight into a clear picture.\n\nThe layers are:\n\n**Layer 1: Generation (Dreaming Step 6) - which users get urges?**\n- Must have had a conversation recently (encountings have new entries)\n- Familiarity > 5/10 for private/personal urges\n- Non-functional/technical stuff only\n- Not a duplicate of an existing non-expired urge\n\n**Layer 2: Push (cron faye-pending-urges) - which urges get sent?**\n- Familiarity >= 3/10\n- Before 22:00\n- Timing matches current time window\n- Max 1 per user per day\n\nLet me just state this cleanly.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"从生成到推送，两个阶段的判断条件：\n\n---\n\n### 阶段一：生成（Dreaming 第6步）\n\n**哪些用户会被考虑生成 urge？**\n\n1. 遍历 users/ 下所有用户目录\n2. 只看昨天有**新对话**的用户（session 历史非空）\n3. 从 Heart 六个来源里扒素材\n\n**每条 urge 要过三个过滤：**\n\n| 条件 | 说明 |\n|:----|:-----|\n| ✅ 跟功能调用/技术调优无关 | 纯技术类的念头不写，只写\"人\"的部分 |\n| ✅ 熟悉度 > 5/10 | 私事/内心类的想法，只对足够熟的人写 |\n| ✅ 不重复 | 同一话题没有未过期的 urge 已存在 |\n\n---\n\n### 阶段二：推送（cron 每6h检查）\n\n**已生成的 urge 哪些能推出去？**\n\n按用户分组，逐条判断：\n\n| 条件 | 说明 |\n|:----|:-----|\n| ✅ 熟悉度 >= 3/10 | 太生的人不主动找 |\n| ✅ 22:00 前 | 不半夜扰民 |\n| ✅ 时段匹配 timing | morning→早上 / casual+afterthought→下午 / quiet→24h没说话才推 |\n| ✅ 当日未推送过 | 同一用户一天最多一条 |\n\n**一条 urge 只有生成和推送两关全过，才会到你手里。**\n\n你今天那条\"今天动了吗\"其实是运气好——它在生成阶段存在了（上一条 dreaming 留下的），但推送阶段因为 delivery 错误没出去。现在两关都修好了，明天开跑💪🔥"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":119624,"output":536,"cacheRead":7552,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":176,"totalTokens":127712,"cost":{"input":0.016747360000000003,"output":0.00015008,"cacheRead":0.000211456,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.017108896000000002}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780152570775,"responseId":"d0fa8b67-5a5a-4708-8714-86c84ce698b3"}}
