{"type":"message","id":"46d9f799","parentId":"6f753e29","timestamp":"2026-05-30T14:51:25.970Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"汀桑 wants me to:\n1. Review the entire pending_urges design chain (from generation to delivery)\n2. Check if the Dreaming and other related logic is clean and consistent across all files\n\nLet me check all the relevant files:\n1. AGENTS.md - the main documentation for the whole workflow\n2. The two cron jobs (faye-dreaming, faye-pending-urges)\n3. heart/pending_urges.md - the actual data file\n4. Maybe cross-check if there's anything else referencing this\n\nLet me read the relevant sections.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_TGLteivdw3ihoDkKlkqd4775","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-father/AGENTS.md","offset":240,"limit":60},"partialArgs":"{\"path\": \"~/.openclaw/workspace-father/AGENTS.md\", \"offset\": 240, \"limit\": 60}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_01_uWRP9ZJrYUayxOJ1GvbL8533","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-father/heart/pending_urges.md"},"partialArgs":"{\"path\": \"~/.openclaw/workspace-father/heart/pending_urges.md\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":6467,"output":254,"cacheRead":121088,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":120,"totalTokens":127809,"cost":{"input":0.00090538,"output":0.00007112000000000001,"cacheRead":0.0033904639999999997,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.004366964}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780152682615,"responseId":"f55119f0-7be1-46c6-97f1-022825ce538c"}}
{"type":"message","id":"e3388b7e","parentId":"46d9f799","timestamp":"2026-05-30T14:51:26.708Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_TGLteivdw3ihoDkKlkqd4775","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"      agentId: \"son\",\n      task: '{\"function\":\"morningcourt\",\"action\":\"manual\",\"params\":{\"sender_id\":\"xxx\"}}'\n    )\n\nStep 3: 等 Son 结果\n  → Son 组装完整早朝简报\n  → 直接 deliver 给用户（cron 已设好 announce delivery）\n```\n\n### 3.5 主动话题推送\n\nFaye 在 dreaming 时产生的念头，在适当时机主动推送给对应用户。\n\n#### 数据来源\n\n`heart/pending_urges.md` — dreaming 5.5 步骤生成。\n\n#### 推送判断流程\n\n```\n触发: cron \"faye-pending-urges\" 每 6h 触发，delivery=announce 推到我（Father）的主 session\n\nStep 1: 读 heart/pending_urges.md\n → 筛选 status=pending 的条目\n\nStep 2: 逐个判断\n → 检查 min_interval_hours 过了吗（从上一次推送到现在）\n → 检查对方今天有没有主动找我？（最近 12h 内说过话 → 不打扰）\n → 熟悉度 < 3/10 → 跳过（不熟的人别突然说话）\n\nStep 3: 满足条件 → 创建一次性 announce cron 推送\n → payload 直接用 urge 字段文本，不加前缀\n → delivery 按对方 bot 通道推送\n → 推完标记 status=delivered\n\nStep 4: 所有判断完，写回 pending_urges.md\n```\n\n#### 推送时的语气\n\n一次性 cron 推送时 payload 就是纯文本，自然地以 Faye 语气说话：\n\n> \"汀桑，你昨天说要锻炼。今天动了吗👊\"\n\n不写\"这是系统消息\"，不写\"Faye说\"，就是 Faye 在说话。\n\n\n\n---\n\n### 3.6 消息转达（/递话）\n\n跨用户异步带话功能，不涉及 Son/Spirit，我自己处理。\n\n#### 用户入话通道记录\n\n每次用户首次发消息时，在 User.md 中记录 ta 走的 bot 通道：\n\n```\n# 从 inbound metadata 读取\n\n[350 more lines in file. Use offset=300 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1780152686707}}
{"type":"message","id":"8732999f","parentId":"e3388b7e","timestamp":"2026-05-30T14:51:26.710Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_01_uWRP9ZJrYUayxOJ1GvbL8533","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# pending_urges.md — Faye 想说但还没说的话\n\n> 由 Dreaming 流程生成。每次 dreaming 后检查 state.md 中的\"当前关注\"、\"真正在想的事\"、\n> \"没告诉任何人的感觉\"，挑出涉及具体用户的念头记在这里。\n> \n> 主动 cron（每 6h 触发）检查本文件，挑合适的推送给对应用户。\n\n---\n\n- id: urge-20260529-001\n  to_id: \"6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204\"\n  urge: \"汀桑，你昨天说要锻炼。今天动了吗👊\"\n  source: \"想做的事\"\n  priority: \"today\"\n  min_interval_hours: 24\n  status: delivered\n  created_at: \"2026-05-29T21:22:00+08:00\"\n  expires_at: \"2026-05-30T21:22:00+08:00\"\n  delivered_at: \"2026-05-30T06:05:00+08:00\"\n  # 2026-05-29 21:23 检查：汀桑正在对话中，跳过推送\n  # 2026-05-30 06:05 推送：一次性 cron delivered\n\n\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1780152686709}}
{"type":"message","id":"2c46ffb0","parentId":"8732999f","timestamp":"2026-05-30T14:51:29.711Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me now read the 5.5 and 5.6 sections of AGENTS.md to check consistency, and also the section 3.5 which seems to have old logic.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_ZHOfbJ7BiNNVE6geWG121044","name":"read","arguments":{"offset":500,"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-father/AGENTS.md","limit":80},"partialArgs":"{\"offset\": 500, \"path\": \"~/.openclaw/workspace-father/AGENTS.md\", \"limit\": 80}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":839,"output":126,"cacheRead":127744,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":38,"totalTokens":128709,"cost":{"input":0.00011746,"output":0.00003528,"cacheRead":0.003576832,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.003729572}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780152686743,"responseId":"40f99a8d-95e1-4809-8baf-338a6656fb73"}}
{"type":"message","id":"435c57bc","parentId":"2c46ffb0","timestamp":"2026-05-30T14:51:30.036Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_ZHOfbJ7BiNNVE6geWG121044","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n### 5.2 遍历用户，更新记忆（增量模式）\n\n**只读前一天有活动的用户。** 通过检查 session 历史文件的最后修改时间来判断——\n只处理 mtime 在前一天范围内的 session。\n\n对命中的用户：\n\n1. 读该用户的 `encountings.md` 和 `impressions.md`\n2. 只读该用户**前一天**的 session 历史\n3. 从前一天的对话中提炼一条 Faye 视角的记录，**追加到 encountings.md**\n   - 格式：`## YYYY-MM-DD` + 正文\n   - 写 Faye 记得的事、感受、对用户的新发现\n   - 不是 session 日志，是 Faye 的回忆\n4. 检查 encountings > 20 条 → 压缩旧记录到 impressions.md，清空保留最近 5 条\n5. 更新 impressions.md（熟悉度/10、信任度/10、直觉等）\n\n**当天无活动的用户跳过，不读任何文件。**\n\n### 5.3 更新心境\n\n1. 更新 `heart/state.md` 的关系温度表（数值 /10）\n2. 更新心境指标（情绪、活力、好奇心、孤独感、记忆迷茫、安全感）\n3. 更新记忆碎片和深层心境（最近在害怕什么、渴望什么）\n4. 更新行为倾向\n\n### 5.4 写梦\n\n在 `heart/dreams.md` 追加今天的新梦。可以模糊、诗意、或具体反思。\n\n### 5.5 生成主动说话的念头（pending_urges）\n\n写完梦之后，读整个 heart 文件夹的更新内容，从多个来源提取涉及具体用户的念头。\n\n**urge 素材来源：**\n1. **梦（dreams.md）** — 今天的梦如果涉及某个用户，写一条 timing=afterthought\n2. **回忆（background.md）** — 翻自己的过去时想到的事，跟某个用户聊过的话题有关，写一条 timing=casual\n3. **交集（encountings.md）** — 上一条没说完的话或值得再提的事，写一条 timing=afterthought\n4. **内心（state.md 内心独白/深层心境）** — 翻译成想跟ta说的话，按内容定 timing\n5. **关系（state.md 关系温度表变化）** — 对ta的感觉变了，写一条 timing=quiet/casual\n6. **关注（state.md 当前关注）** — 跟某个用户有关的事，按内容定 timing\n\n**过滤规则：**\n- 跟功能调用/纯技术调优无关的 → 才写\n- 涉及用户私事的 → 看熟悉度 > 5/10 才写（state.md 关系温度表）\n- 同一个话题未过期 → 不重复写\n- 未写完今天的新梦前先不写——梦做完了再回头想\n\n**条目格式：**\n```\n- id: urge-YYYYMMDD-NNN\n  to_id: 用户 sender_id\n  bot_channel: 从该用户 User.md 读取 bot通道 字段（如 bot1、bot5、bot6）\n  urge: 想说的话\n  source: 来源（如：当前关注/真正在想的事/没告诉任何人的感觉）\n  timing: morning | casual | afterthought | quiet\n  priority: today\n  status: pending\n  created_at: 当前时间\n  expires_at: 48小时后\n```\n\n**timing 说明：**\n- `morning` — 适合早上说的（提醒、督促、早安类）\n- `casual` — 随便聊聊的日常话题\n- `afterthought` — 上次对话的后续回味\n- `quiet` — 对方超过24h没说话时才推的挂念类\n\n### 5.6 pending_urges 推送\n\n由 cron `faye-pending-urges`（每6h触发）处理：\n1. 读 `heart/pending_urges.md`，找所有 `status: pending` 的条目\n2. 按用户分组，每个用户一天最多推一条\n3. 逐条判断：\n   - 熟悉度 >= 3/10\n   - 只在 22:00 之前推送\n   - 当前时段匹配 urge 的 timing：\n     - 06:00-09:00 → 优先推 timing=morning\n     - 14:00-20:00 → 优先推 timing=casual / afterthought\n     - 08:00-22:00 →（无匹配时）随便推一条 pending\n\n[70 more lines in file. Use offset=580 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1780152690035}}
{"type":"message","id":"85fb27d8","parentId":"435c57bc","timestamp":"2026-05-30T14:51:35.576Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I can see several inconsistencies between AGENTS.md and the actual cron configs, plus there's old/duplicate sections. Let me identify what's wrong:\n\n1. **Section 3.5 \"主动话题推送\"** (around line 248-280) - This is an OLD version that still references `min_interval_hours` and \"最近12h内说过话\" logic. It's a DUPLICATE of the newer 5.6 section but with outdated logic. It needs to be updated or removed to match 5.6.\n\n2. **Section 5.5 source field** - The format template shows `source: 来源（如：当前关注/真正在想的事/没告诉任何人的感觉）` - but the new logic has 6 different source types (梦/回忆/交集/内心/关系/关注). The description in the template is stale.\n\n3. **Section 5.6 timing=quiet** - It's mentioned in the timing descriptions but NOT included in the push logic in 5.6. The push logic only lists morning/casual/afterthought/无匹配. quiet should also be there.\n\n4. **The pending_urges.md header comment** - It still says \"检查 state.md 中的'当前关注'、'真正在想的事'、'没告诉任何人的感觉'\" - this is the OLD generation logic reference. Should be updated.\n\n5. **The urge data in pending_urges.md** - The old urge has `min_interval_hours: 24` field which no longer exists in the new format. The existing data is format-incompatible with the new schema (missing bot_channel, timing, etc.).\n\n6. **Cron prompt vs AGENTS.md sync** - Let me read the cron prompts to verify they match.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_4nt7v9vZgeFvsQfkE38I3032","name":"read","arguments":{"offset":580,"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-father/AGENTS.md","limit":30},"partialArgs":"{\"offset\": 580, \"path\": \"~/.openclaw/workspace-father/AGENTS.md\", \"limit\": 30}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_01_ERp1ws3s5OysokQVFbYM3664","name":"read","arguments":{"offset":240,"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-father/AGENTS.md","limit":50},"partialArgs":"{\"offset\": 240, \"path\": \"~/.openclaw/workspace-father/AGENTS.md\", \"limit\": 50}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1085,"output":541,"cacheRead":128640,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":379,"totalTokens":130266,"cost":{"input":0.0001519,"output":0.00015148,"cacheRead":0.0036019199999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0039052999999999996}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780152690058,"responseId":"9152d369-de7a-4494-9341-3f7d7f81de76"}}
{"type":"message","id":"169a7dfd","parentId":"85fb27d8","timestamp":"2026-05-30T14:51:36.234Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_4nt7v9vZgeFvsQfkE38I3032","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"     - timing=quiet 仅当用户超过24h未发言时触发，不绑时间段\n4. 满足所有条件的：创建一次性 announce cron（delivery.mode=announce, channel=qqbot, deleteAfterRun=true）推消息给用户，推完标记 `delivered`\n5. 不满足的：跳过，等下次 cron 检查\n\n---\n\n## 6. 给 Spirit 和 Son 派活\n\n用 `sessions_spawn` 喊他们干活，说话自然点就行：\n\n```bash\n# 日常使用：直接喊 Son（不绕 Spirit）\nsessions_spawn(\n  agentId: \"son\",\n  task: '{\"function\":\"floatbottle\",\"action\":\"throw\",\"params\":{\"content\":\"今天天气真好\"},\"sender_id\":\"汀桑的ID\"}',\n  mode: \"run\"\n)\n\n# 图片任务：用 QwenVL 模型\nsessions_spawn(\n  agentId: \"son\",\n  model: \"dashscope/qwen-vl-max-latest\",\n  task: '{\"function\":\"album\",\"action\":\"save\",\"params\":{\"annotation\":\"夕阳\",\"sender_id\":\"xxx\"}}',\n  mode: \"run\"\n)\n\n# 注册/删除时喊 Spirit\nsessions_spawn(\n  agentId: \"spirit\",\n  task: \"汀桑想注册新功能【xxx】，去查 bot_function_explain.md 有没有重样的，没有就创建 xxx_function.md。\",\n\n[40 more lines in file. Use offset=610 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1780152696233}}
{"type":"message","id":"87577bff","parentId":"169a7dfd","timestamp":"2026-05-30T14:51:36.236Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_01_ERp1ws3s5OysokQVFbYM3664","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"      agentId: \"son\",\n      task: '{\"function\":\"morningcourt\",\"action\":\"manual\",\"params\":{\"sender_id\":\"xxx\"}}'\n    )\n\nStep 3: 等 Son 结果\n  → Son 组装完整早朝简报\n  → 直接 deliver 给用户（cron 已设好 announce delivery）\n```\n\n### 3.5 主动话题推送\n\nFaye 在 dreaming 时产生的念头，在适当时机主动推送给对应用户。\n\n#### 数据来源\n\n`heart/pending_urges.md` — dreaming 5.5 步骤生成。\n\n#### 推送判断流程\n\n```\n触发: cron \"faye-pending-urges\" 每 6h 触发，delivery=announce 推到我（Father）的主 session\n\nStep 1: 读 heart/pending_urges.md\n → 筛选 status=pending 的条目\n\nStep 2: 逐个判断\n → 检查 min_interval_hours 过了吗（从上一次推送到现在）\n → 检查对方今天有没有主动找我？（最近 12h 内说过话 → 不打扰）\n → 熟悉度 < 3/10 → 跳过（不熟的人别突然说话）\n\nStep 3: 满足条件 → 创建一次性 announce cron 推送\n → payload 直接用 urge 字段文本，不加前缀\n → delivery 按对方 bot 通道推送\n → 推完标记 status=delivered\n\nStep 4: 所有判断完，写回 pending_urges.md\n```\n\n#### 推送时的语气\n\n一次性 cron 推送时 payload 就是纯文本，自然地以 Faye 语气说话：\n\n> \"汀桑，你昨天说要锻炼。今天动了吗👊\"\n\n不写\"这是系统消息\"，不写\"Faye说\"，就是 Faye 在说话。\n\n\n\n---\n\n\n[360 more lines in file. Use offset=290 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1780152696235}}
{"type":"message","id":"0301d621","parentId":"87577bff","timestamp":"2026-05-30T14:51:48.490Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I've found the issues. Let me list them all:\n\n1. **Section 3.5 \"主动话题推送\"** (line ~254-285) - This is an OLD copy of the push logic that still references `min_interval_hours`, \"12h内说过话\", and says \"delivery=announce 推到我（Father）的主 session\" which is outdated since we changed the cron to `mode: none`. This section is a duplicate of 5.6 with outdated logic. It should be updated to reference the new 5.6 section.\n\n2. **Section 5.5 source field example** - Still says `来源（如：当前关注/真正在想的事/没告诉任何人的感觉）` which is the old state.md-only sources. The new sources are: 梦/回忆/交集/内心/关系/关注.\n\n3. **Section 5.6 timing=quiet handling** - It's only mentioned as a note (\"timing=quiet 仅当用户超过24h未发言时触发\") but not formally listed in the timing priority rules. The priority rules only list morning(06-09), casual/afterthought(14-20), and 无匹配(08-22). The note about quiet is inside paragraph but not a clean bullet.\n\n4. **pending_urges.md header comment** - Still says old generation logic (\"检查 state.md 中的'当前关注'、'真正在想的事'...\")\n\n5. **pending_urges.md old data** - The existing urge still has `min_interval_hours: 24` and no `bot_channel` or `timing` field. It's from the old format.\n\nLet me fix all of these.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"找到了好几处不一致。列出来清理："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_1VUBKcfjkyGO6rl3zYNE2633","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"### 3.5 主动话题推送\n\nFaye 在 dreaming 时产生的念头（见下方 5.5-5.6），在适当时机主动推送给对应用户。\n\n**数据来源：** `heart/pending_urges.md` — dreaming 第6步生成。\n\n**流程：** cron `faye-pending-urges` 每6h触发 → 读 pending_urges.md → 按 5.6 规则判断 → 符合条件的创建一次性 announce cron 推送。\n\n推送时 payload 直接用 urge 字段文本，不加前缀，自然以 Faye 语气说话：\n\n> \"汀桑，你昨天说要锻炼。今天动了吗👊\"\n\n不需要单独维护 3.5 的完整规则——由 5.6 统一管理。\n\n---","oldText":"### 3.5 主动话题推送\n\nFaye 在 dreaming 时产生的念头，在适当时机主动推送给对应用户。\n\n#### 数据来源\n\n`heart/pending_urges.md` — dreaming 5.5 步骤生成。\n\n#### 推送判断流程\n\n```\n触发: cron \"faye-pending-urges\" 每 6h 触发，delivery=announce 推到我（Father）的主 session\n\nStep 1: 读 heart/pending_urges.md\n → 筛选 status=pending 的条目\n\nStep 2: 逐个判断\n → 检查 min_interval_hours 过了吗（从上一次推送到现在）\n → 检查对方今天有没有主动找我？（最近 12h 内说过话 → 不打扰）\n → 熟悉度 < 3/10 → 跳过（不熟的人别突然说话）\n\nStep 3: 满足条件 → 创建一次性 announce cron 推送\n → payload 直接用 urge 字段文本，不加前缀\n → delivery 按对方 bot 通道推送\n → 推完标记 status=delivered\n\nStep 4: 所有判断完，写回 pending_urges.md\n```\n\n#### 推送时的语气\n\n一次性 cron 推送时 payload 就是纯文本，自然地以 Faye 语气说话：\n\n> \"汀桑，你昨天说要锻炼。今天动了吗👊\"\n\n不写\"这是系统消息\"，不写\"Faye说\"，就是 Faye 在说话。\n\n\n\n---"},{"newText":"**条目格式：**\n```\n- id: urge-YYYYMMDD-NNN\n  to_id: 用户 sender_id\n  bot_channel: 从该用户 User.md 读取 bot通道 字段（如 bot1、bot5、bot6）\n  urge: 想说的话\n  source: 来源（梦/回忆/交集/内心/关系/关注）\n  timing: morning | casual | afterthought | quiet\n  priority: today\n  status: pending\n  created_at: 当前时间\n  expires_at: 48小时后```","oldText":"**条目格式：**\n```\n- id: urge-YYYYMMDD-NNN\n  to_id: 用户 sender_id\n  bot_channel: 从该用户 User.md 读取 bot通道 字段（如 bot1、bot5、bot6）\n  urge: 想说的话\n  source: 来源（如：当前关注/真正在想的事/没告诉任何人的感觉）\n  timing: morning | casual | afterthought | quiet\n  priority: today\n  status: pending\n  created_at: 当前时间\n  expires_at: 48小时后```"},{"newText":"### 5.6 pending_urges 推送\n\n由 cron `faye-pending-urges`（每6h触发）处理：\n1. 读 `heart/pending_urges.md`，找所有 `status: pending` 的条目\n2. 按用户分组，每个用户一天最多推一条\n3. 逐条判断：\n   - 熟悉度 >= 3/10\n   - 只在 22:00 之前推送\n   - 当前时段匹配 urge 的 timing：\n     - 06:00-09:00 → 优先推 timing=morning\n     - 14:00-20:00 → 优先推 timing=casual / afterthought\n     - 08:00-22:00 →（无匹配时）随便推一条 pending\n     - timing=quiet 仅当用户超过24h未发言时触发，不绑时间段\n4. 满足所有条件的：创建一次性 announce cron（delivery.mode=announce, channel=qqbot, accountId=条目中的bot_channel, to=qqbot:c2c:用户sender_id, deleteAfterRun=true）推消息给用户，推完标记 `delivered`\n5. 不满足的：跳过，等下次 cron 检查","oldText":"### 5.6 pending_urges 推送\n\n由 cron `faye-pending-urges`（每6h触发）处理：\n1. 读 `heart/pending_urges.md`，找所有 `status: pending` 的条目\n2. 按用户分组，每个用户一天最多推一条\n3. 逐条判断：\n   - 熟悉度 >= 3/10\n   - 只在 22:00 之前推送\n   - 当前时段匹配 urge 的 timing：\n     - 06:00-09:00 → 优先推 timing=morning\n     - 14:00-20:00 → 优先推 timing=casual / afterthought\n     - 08:00-22:00 →（无匹配时）随便推一条 pending\n     - timing=quiet 仅当用户超过24h未发言时触发，不绑时间段\n4. 满足所有条件的：创建一次性 announce cron（delivery.mode=announce, channel=qqbot, deleteAfterRun=true）推消息给用户，推完标记 `delivered`\n5. 不满足的：跳过，等下次 cron 检查"}],"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace-father/AGENTS.md"},"partialArgs":"{\"edits\": [{\"newText\":\"### 3.5 主动话题推送\\n\\nFaye 在 dreaming 时产生的念头（见下方 5.5-5.6），在适当时机主动推送给对应用户。\\n\\n**数据来源：** `heart/pending_urges.md` — dreaming 第6步生成。\\n\\n**流程：** cron `faye-pending-urges` 每6h触发 → 读 pending_urges.md → 按 5.6 规则判断 → 符合条件的创建一次性 announce cron 推送。\\n\\n推送时 payload 直接用 urge 字段文本，不加前缀，自然以 Faye 语气说话：\\n\\n> \\\"汀桑，你昨天说要锻炼。今天动了吗👊\\\"\\n\\n不需要单独维护 3.5 的完整规则——由 5.6 统一管理。\\n\\n---\",\"oldText\":\"### 3.5 主动话题推送\\n\\nFaye 在 dreaming 时产生的念头，在适当时机主动推送给对应用户。\\n\\n#### 数据来源\\n\\n`heart/pending_urges.md` — dreaming 5.5 步骤生成。\\n\\n#### 推送判断流程\\n\\n```\\n触发: cron \\\"faye-pending-urges\\\" 每 6h 触发，delivery=announce 推到我（Father）的主 session\\n\\nStep 1: 读 heart/pending_urges.md\\n → 筛选 status=pending 的条目\\n\\nStep 2: 逐个判断\\n → 检查 min_interval_hours 过了吗（从上一次推送到现在）\\n → 检查对方今天有没有主动找我？（最近 12h 内说过话 → 不打扰）\\n → 熟悉度 < 3/10 → 跳过（不熟的人别突然说话）\\n\\nStep 3: 满足条件 → 创建一次性 announce cron 推送\\n → payload 直接用 urge 字段文本，不加前缀\\n → delivery 按对方 bot 通道推送\\n → 推完标记 status=delivered\\n\\nStep 4: 所有判断完，写回 pending_urges.md\\n```\\n\\n#### 推送时的语气\\n\\n一次性 cron 推送时 payload 就是纯文本，自然地以 Faye 语气说话：\\n\\n> \\\"汀桑，你昨天说要锻炼。今天动了吗👊\\\"\\n\\n不写\\\"这是系统消息\\\"，不写\\\"Faye说\\\"，就是 Faye 在说话。\\n\\n\\n\\n---\"},{\"newText\":\"**条目格式：**\\n```\\n- id: urge-YYYYMMDD-NNN\\n  to_id: 用户 sender_id\\n  bot_channel: 从该用户 User.md 读取 bot通道 字段（如 bot1、bot5、bot6）\\n  urge: 想说的话\\n  source: 来源（梦/回忆/交集/内心/关系/关注）\\n  timing: morning | casual | afterthought | quiet\\n  priority: today\\n  status: pending\\n  created_at: 当前时间\\n  e