{"type":"message","id":"68c50a6b","parentId":"6439c9ed","timestamp":"2026-05-30T14:52:36.940Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user says \"先别改\" - don't change anything yet. They're just showing me the metadata. This seems like they're just confirming the chat_id format `qqbot:c2c:{sender_id}` is correct. The metadata shows `chat_id: \"qqbot:c2c:6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204\"` which matches exactly what we've been using.\n\nThey probably want me to just acknowledge and not make any more changes right now.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"收到。不碰了。\n\n就是想让我确认一下这个 chat_id 格式对吧？—— `qqbot:c2c:6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204`，跟我们写进 cron 里的完全一致🍧"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":136541,"output":168,"cacheRead":3456,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":109,"totalTokens":140165,"cost":{"input":0.019115740000000003,"output":0.000047040000000000004,"cacheRead":0.00009676799999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.019259548000000005}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780152749549,"responseId":"2f601c97-aa86-4c85-832b-744ff912b7d2"}}
