{"type":"message","id":"9989d8be","parentId":"ef445c4d","timestamp":"2026-05-30T14:55:35.895Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"汀桑 is asking for a final confirmation that the pending_urges and dreaming processes are fully repaired and consistent. Let me do a final comprehensive check across all the files and cron jobs to make sure everything is aligned.\n\nLet me think about what the full chain should look like:\n\n1. AGENTS.md - the source of truth for the design\n2. Dreaming cron (faye-dreaming) - runs Step 1-6 at 06:00 daily\n3. Pending-urges cron (faye-pending-urges) - runs every 6h, checks and delivers\n4. heart/pending_urges.md - the data file\n\nI need to verify:\n- Both cron prompts are aligned with AGENTS.md\n- The source-of-truth document is clean and up to date\n- All the fixes we made are in place\n\nLet me do a quick read of the key sections to confirm.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"让我最后全线检查一遍。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_NOqsoZRXTPhIrCvc1y5I7328","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace-father/heart/pending_urges.md"},"partialArgs":"{\"path\": \"/root/.openclaw/workspace-father/heart/pending_urges.md\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_01_AePo4FWsYg3w1IgsSYD69501","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -n \"生成\\|推送\\|dreaming\\|pending_urges\\|urge\\|6. 生成\\|timing\\|bot_channel\\|accountId=条目\" /usr/local/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/concepts/dreaming.md 2>/dev/null | head -5; echo \"---\"; echo \"AGENTS.md pending checks:\"; grep -c \"min_interval_hours\\|12h.*说过话\\|当前关注/真正在想\" /root/.openclaw/workspace-father/AGENTS.md 2>&1; echo \"---\"; echo \"Dreaming cron Step 6 count:\"; grep -c \"第六步：生成 pending_urges\" /root/.openclaw/workspace-father/.openclaw/workspace-state.json 2>/dev/null || echo \"(not relevant)\"","timeout":5},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"grep -n \\\"生成\\\\|推送\\\\|dreaming\\\\|pending_urges\\\\|urge\\\\|6. 生成\\\\|timing\\\\|bot_ch