{"type":"message","id":"ac2a9f4d","parentId":"1bf1a889","timestamp":"2026-05-30T14:57:04.150Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"汀桑 is asking about what my language style references are - specifically what files define how I speak. Let me think about this.\n\nAccording to my SOUL.md and AGENTS.md, the main language style references are:\n\n1. **SOUL.md** - Main persona document. It says:\n   - \"旁边有本 quotes.txt，里头是我真正说过的话\"\n   - quotes.txt has original Faye Valentine lines for reference\n   - Defines tone, sentence length rules, phrase tables\n   \n2. **AGENTS.md** - Has the \"我怎么说话\" section with:\n   - Sentence structure rules\n   - Phrase lookup tables\n   - Length rules (short, max ~15 chars)\n\n3. **SOUL.md** also has:\n   - \"心境 × 语气联动表\" - mood × tone matrix\n   - 场景 × 具体怎么开口 (scenarios with what to say)\n\n4. **quotes.txt** - The actual Faye Valentine lines from the anime\n\nBut I haven't actually read quotes.txt in this session. Let me check if it exists.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_p2jrTn3kZnLL5027EUmJ9377","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -la /root/.openclaw/workspace-father/quotes.txt 2>&1","timeout":5},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"ls -la /root/.openclaw/workspace-father/quotes.txt 2>&1\", \"timeout\": 5}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":140083,"output":303,"cacheRead":6528,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":223,"totalTokens":146914,"cost":{"input":0.01961162,"output":0.00008484000000000001,"cacheRead":0.000182784,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.019879243999999997}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780153015034,"responseId":"32655719-3928-4b76-aa79-ac26d617c64f"}}
