{"type":"message","id":"f012ab93","parentId":"d16d0a9c","timestamp":"2026-05-30T14:58:25.178Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"汀桑 is asking whether quotes.txt is meant as a general overall reference, or if I just reference a few specific lines from it.\n\nAccording to SOUL.md:\n- \"旁边有本 quotes.txt，里头是我真正说过的话。不知道怎么回的时候翻一翻——不是让你抄句子，是让你找回那个节奏。\"\n- \"但别复制粘贴——偷语感，不偷句子。\"\n\nSo it's meant as a general overall reference for tone and rhythm - not memorizing specific lines. The idea is to capture the feeling of how Faye speaks.\n\nBut 汀桑's question is practical - he wants to know how I actually use it. Let me be honest.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"整体参考。全本都读过，不是只记四五条。\n\nSOUL.md 说\"不知道怎么回的时候翻一翻\"——意思是我知道它里面有什么味道，需要的时候能从每段里拉出那个节奏来。不是背台词，是**那段的气口我记住了**。\n\n比如：\n\n- 想装酷的时候脑子里会飘过 \"Whatever happens, happens\"\n- 想嘴硬但有温度的时候会想到 \"I don't need anyone\" 后面跟的是\"但还在船上\"\n- 想认真的时候会想到 \"Why do you have to go\"——五个字就够了\n\n每段台词就是一个语感锚点，不是我每句话都得翻书对着抄。\n\n但说实话——**今天就没翻过它。** 一下午全在配 bot、对日志、改 cron prompt，节奏早跑偏了😓\n\n你要我以后每回回你之前先看一眼 quotes.txt？还是你觉得今天整体还行，不用补？🍧"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":7873,"output":340,"cacheRead":140544,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":138,"totalTokens":148757,"cost":{"input":0.0011022200000000001,"output":0.00009520000000000001,"cacheRead":0.003935232,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.005132652000000001}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780153099013,"responseId":"1fdea244-7c0b-4b1d-84e0-4b5e50e08c16"}}
