{"type":"message","id":"90d8f366","parentId":"33a83ea0","timestamp":"2026-05-30T14:59:43.021Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"汀桑 is testing the system. The metadata confirms the chat_id format `qqbot:c2c:6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204` which matches what we configured in the pending_urges cron delivery.\n\nThis seems like he's just acknowledging the chat_id format is correct and saying he's testing. Let me give a casual response.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"嗯？测试啥？bot6 通了、bot5 也来人了、pending_urges 改好了、衰减加上了。\n\n现在就等明天 06:00 dreaming 跑第一次，看第6步能不能憋出点话来。\n\n——还是你另有什么要测的？😏"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":2533,"output":146,"cacheRead":148096,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":83,"totalTokens":150775,"cost":{"input":0.00035462000000000004,"output":0.00004088,"cacheRead":0.004146688,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.004542188}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780153180194,"responseId":"01d628be-74c7-45cc-b2b8-016d2a085934"}}
