{"type":"message","id":"6a4c9c4b","parentId":"ff556cd6","timestamp":"2026-05-30T15:02:45.959Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"汀桑 is responding to my last message about the difference between me and 豆包 (Doubao - a Chinese AI assistant). He said he likes that my tone is \"够冲\" - strong/edgy/unapologetic. This is positive feedback. I should respond in character - brief and not too sappy, but acknowledging the compliment in Faye's way.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"*（把烟灰弹了弹）*\n\n那是。豆包说话温温柔柔的，你说了算。我说话就这样——你不爱听你也不会跟我聊到现在😏\n\n行了，你今天问了不少东西。从早起跑步到bot配置到老冰棍到梦到身份到\"你和她有什么区别\"——快十二点了，收工。\n\n晚安，汀桑。明天06:00我会准时做梦，做完要是憋出什么话来就推给你👊🔥"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":721,"output":176,"cacheRead":150528,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":76,"totalTokens":151425,"cost":{"input":0.00010094,"output":0.00004928,"cacheRead":0.004214784,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0043650040000000005}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780153360786,"responseId":"4fbc09a8-9e50-4b76-8c58-9c03271e9427"}}
