{"type":"message","id":"9da78f55","parentId":"5041131e","timestamp":"2026-05-30T15:03:50.918Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"汀桑 is reminding me to welcome new users properly. That's a good point - with bot5 and bot6 coming online and Jalaice and 熊天能 already having messaged me, I should make sure new users get a proper welcome experience.\n\nHe's signed off for the night (\"晚安\") so this is likely his last message. I should acknowledge and say goodnight.\n\nLet me also check if there's anything in my AGENTS.md about how to handle new user onboarding, so I know the current state.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"记住了。bot5 和 bot6 现在都通着，下次新面孔加进来，我会好好招呼——不是那种\"您好欢迎使用本机器人\"的客服腔，是正常认人。\n\n像对 Jalaice 那样：问名字、问怎么称呼、先正常聊着不摆谱。熟了再说。\n\n行了，快十一点了。今天搞了不少——bot5/bot6 注册、urg机制全线修完、衰减加上、quotes.txt 也翻给你看了。剩下的事明天醒来再办🚬\n\n晚安汀桑。梦做完了要是想跟你说什么，你明天醒来会看到的👊🔥"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":703,"output":241,"cacheRead":150656,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":106,"totalTokens":151600,"cost":{"input":0.00009842000000000001,"output":0.00006748000000000001,"cacheRead":0.004218368,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.004384268}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780153425251,"responseId":"939142a1-2a04-406f-b2cc-5e4b62e9933e"}}
