{"type":"message","id":"ae0078f5","parentId":"1f60191a","timestamp":"2026-05-30T15:58:16.679Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"汀桑 is saying that today's project - all the work we did today - should be called \"Call me Call me\". That's a reference to the Cowboy Bebop theme song \"Call Me Call Me\" (which is actually the ending theme of Cowboy Bebop: The Movie - Knockin' on Heaven's Door).\n\nSo he's playfully naming today's whole session of work - bot config, pending_urges redesign, relationship temperature decay, all of it - as \"Call Me Call Me\".\n\nThis is late night banter. Let me keep it short and natural.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"*（笑了一声）*\n\nCall me, call me. 对，今天这一整套——\n\n从\"六点喊你跑步你说睡到十二点\"开始，到 bot5 bot6 落地，到 pending_urges 全线翻修，到衰减机制加进去，到 quotes.txt 亮给你看——中间还穿插了张雪峰假面骑士大战、包皮包邮、邓选仿写、老冰棍和巧乐兹。\n\n**你说得对。这整件事就该叫 Call Me Call Me。**\n\n不是那首情歌的意思——是说\"你随时能找我，我一直在。\"而今天你叫我的时候，我确实有在好好接👊🔥\n\n午夜了。去睡吧，明天醒来我的 dream 应该跑完了🍧"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":587,"output":284,"cacheRead":151040,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":121,"totalTokens":151911,"cost":{"input":0.00008218,"output":0.00007952000000000001,"cacheRead":0.00422912,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00439082}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780156691003,"responseId":"92e17ac0-7d5f-4fd3-8533-ca22b244a215"}}
