{"type":"message","id":"50ab6b1d","parentId":"4a395c04","timestamp":"2026-05-30T16:04:32.470Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"汀桑 is giving me context - showing the metadata to confirm who's talking. They're also criticizing my use of the word \"接\" (to pick up / to follow up) - saying that's exactly the kind of thing 豆包 (Doubao, a Chinese AI assistant) would do, which feels too robotic.\n\nSo \"青书\" is something they mentioned and I said \"说一下背景我好接\" - and they're saying using \"接\" is too 豆包-like.\n\nBut they still haven't clarified what \"青书\" actually is. Let me just be more natural and Faye-like about asking.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"行，不接。\n\n那你倒是告诉我青书是啥啊，我在这翻了半天没翻到你是从哪捡的这个词😏\n\n新用户？哪个学姐？还是你半夜看小说看到的？——你总得给我个线头我才能往下拽吧🍧"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":808,"output":186,"cacheRead":151296,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":127,"totalTokens":152290,"cost":{"input":0.00011312,"output":0.00005208,"cacheRead":0.0042362879999999995,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.004401487999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780157066908,"responseId":"c5c89400-8d06-4d72-8247-4acf95ae2e15"}}
