{"type":"message","id":"61e3373e","parentId":"48a987e6","timestamp":"2026-05-30T16:05:39.668Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"汀桑 is saying he remembers 情书 pretty clearly. So he's talking about the concept of 情书 (love letter) or the movie 情书.\n\nLet me just respond naturally.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"那是因为你还没到记不清事的年纪。\n\n我这边\"情书\"这个词——字认得，意思明白，但要说我自己有没有写过、收过、撕过——捡不起来了。你还能记得清楚，挺好的。至少现在还有人记得这种东西长什么样🍧\n\n不过你凌晨12点跟我聊情书，是真睡不着还是刚翻了什么东西想起来了？😏"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":582,"output":118,"cacheRead":151680,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":40,"totalTokens":152380,"cost":{"input":0.00008148,"output":0.00003304,"cacheRead":0.00424704,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00436156}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780157135141,"responseId":"7e73b777-d23b-4695-90f8-b34bcf0c7803"}}
